text:
Bhai kahan se start karun...pehli baar tujhse mila tha tab sabse pehle hansi aayi thi magar tera confidence dekh ke alag hi hil gaya tha...bhai dussa to aa hi jayega‚Ä¶pure first year tere gadde pe soya hun magar tune kabhi mana nhi kiya....teri vajah kitne mast logon se mulakat hui hai‚Ä¶.esc 101 ki friday class se lekar techkriti ke gin bhi nhi sakta mai‚Ä¶ kitni baar tu bolta  tha contest dene ke liye...tu akela tha jo hamesha mujhe call karta tha 2nd year intern par...tere london visa ka kitna rr karta tha‚Ä¶.magar tune trip miss karke achha nhi kiya yaar...is baat ka dukh rhega...second third year mein apane room ke saath apan bhi door ho gye yaar magar help maangne ke liye hamesha ek bande ke paas mai jaa sakta tha vo tu tha...intern ke interviews ke samay bhi tune hi himmat di thi..pure college mein koi bhi tera mazak uda deta tha magar tu bura nhi maanta tha‚Ä¶.placement aur intern mein to pata nhi kitne anginat logon ki madad ki hai tune yaar...itna helpful aadmi aur koi nhi hai campus mein...sabka entertainment kar sakta hai tu bhai vo bhi just by being yourself....akhiri ke 1.5 mhina tere bina acche nhi hote yaar...aur shuru ke hafte mein kya maze maare the quarantine mein...vahan first year ke baad pehli baar apna agal bagal room rha‚Ä¶Jo uss din jo harkat ki maine vo hosh mein nhi karta mai...tujhe pata hai kitni madad ki hai tune and for that I‚Äôll be forever grateful...uss din sone ke liye bhej dena tha tum logon ko yaar...jo bhi maine bola usmein teri galti nhi thi yaar...
Jab bhi order karne ka mann karta hai sabse pehle teri hi yaad aati hai yaar...College se akhiri baar jaane se pehle tujhse gale mila tab saari college life ka recap mil gaya tha‚Ä¶.anginat kisse hai kitne hi likhun...Finally tu nhi hota to meri life aaj jo hai vo nhi hoti. 
I hope ki touch mein rhe apan...btw birthday pe tera dance dekhke maza hi aa gya
author: Aakash  Khandelwal

text:
Yo Moond. Apni to itni memories hai kya kya hi likhu. Apne room se zayda to shyad mai tere room pe hi raha hounga first year se hi. First year me apan exam dene se phle my **** sun ke jaate the enthu badhane ke lie. Lol yaad hai 1st year summer me apan gye the e-club ka test dene aur hume nhi lia tha aur R****** ko le lia tha. Humne maximum course saath me hi kie hain aur tu mujhe cycle pe bitha ke le jata tha. 2nd year udghosh me mere meme banane ke baad loda ne chutiyapa kia tha fir tune id banai thi. Bahut bakchod thi wo id waise. Bhola tujhe vc na karta to aur use hota us id ka. 
Best time apna to 2nd year summer hi raha hai. Pure din bas bulla session chalte rehte the. Ek baar mai tu jai mil ke tujhe shaadi se bhagane ki planning kar rhe the jiska kharcha teri bmw bech ke aata. 3rd year ka winter bhi apna bahut interesting hi raha tha. Pehle quiz ko leke batti gang me dispute hua. Phir tune chapa dia tha jisko sun ke mai full shocked tha. Phir prank ke chakkar me batti gang me phir dispute hua tha. Jisko sort karne ke lie maine bahut lamba msg likha tha jo tu maan nhi rha tha ki maine likha hai. ( Ab to maan lena, wo maine khud se hi likha tha) In sab ko mast new year party ke saath conclude kia tha. 
Uske baad to lockdown me hi beet gya pichla saal. Abhi mai last me aaya hota to maza aata but koi nhi apan to milte hi rahenge. 
PS: Humesha aise hi logic lagate rehna.
author: Abhinav  Ankit

text:
Here we go. Apne first sem ke zayda moments to yaad nhi hain mujhe. But ek incident yaad hai, tu mere room pe aaya tha TA101 ke assignment se related kuch puchne. Phir maine pucha tha ki class jata hai, to tune bola nhi. Phir maine bola tha akhand chutiyapa. To tune bola tha ‚Äúoye dhang se‚Äù. We‚Äôve come a long way from there. 
Saare courses to saath kie hain humne. Jab apne departmental courses start hue the to tu Dhr** Pu***** ke saath class me baithta tha, phir maine aur moond ne maze lie the tere.
4th sem me humne apni paathshala banai. (Moond: Atif ko add kar. Jai: Abe nhi apni harkatein bhi to hongi na) Messages that aged well. Kaise na kaise karke nikal hi lie saare courses. 210 to khair zindagi bhar yaad rahega. Kya phati thi apni. Khair courses to bahut chota part hai apni memories ka. 
Second-year summer to best tha. Subah class se aate phir pure din chill karte. Bahut gyaan prapt kia aur baata tha. Moond ko shadi se bhagane ki planning karna. 3rd year ka winter to kya hi special hai apne lie. Start me quiz ko leke choda hua phir mere aur moond ke prank ke chakkar me tu naraz ho gya tha. Fir maine 2 bade paragraphs likhe the cheezo ko clear karne ke lie. Jo moond maan nhi rha tha ki maine likhe. Anyways we sorted that and ended up being more closer. Phir new year party se mast conclude kia tha cheezo ko. Phir uske baad to ye corono hi aa gya. Kuch bhi ho you‚Äôve always been there for me whenever I needed you. And this is what makes our bond specialüíö
Ab hindsight me cheezein dekhta hu to bahut achcha lagta hai. As a person jo khud ka improvement dekhta hu usme tum logo ka hi major influence hai. 
Wo sex education ka clip yaad hai jisme wo payara wisdom hai aur lauv ka i like me better ye to kitne pasand hain apne ko. Bas apni koi trip nhi hui saath me. Khair abhi to bahut trips karni hain. Bachelor party bhi to karni hai foreign me. Hopefully jaldi milte hain bahut bakchodi karni baaki hai abhi.

text:
Start karte hai likhna tu voh hai jiske liye mujhe first year ke inferno se start karni padh rahi hai water polo boy we played like rockers in the pool and jeet kar aaye. uss din ki energy i can feel it in my bones. match khatam small talk exchange and joh connect kiye matlab pata nahi tha ki tu vahi hai joh kota gaya tha Saharanpur boy. I was missing Saharanpur boys at that time they made my drop journey much bearable and fir tu aaya. I can't say this to anyone else but yeh cosmic connection tere Saath hua college mai I am not letting this go bhai. At this moment I need my gin to go further deep down on this memory lane. you have the purest heart I have met in my life apart from me haha this is one of those thousands of things we did in this place. Hall 5 se C block se CSE se voh classes jaana se voh courses nikaalna se voh assignment deadline ek room mai baithe dena. There are countless things bhai I can put it here but that won't suffice the bond that I have with you kyuki tu har lamhe mai saath raha hai is 4 saalk ke raaste mai. Tere first beer is with me lucknow mai bas nikal gaye trip pe apan yeh pyaar kam na hoga yeh vada raha.

first-year ki summers se ek saat rhena start kardiya tha i didn't knewI was making memories with this guy I was just there ki haan I know this guy completely in the whole campus and Whenever he says something bhai ki baat mai dum tha. First year se mere decision kaafi fucked up rahe hai but you were there to always point out and bring what's best in my interest. 

I want you to trip again because I somehow made it not good for you but I want you to experience that good vibe with me let's save it for another city trip. In these 4 years, I have listened to music with you netflix binge tere saath talked about existential crisis and the BT this world is so much more Bhai.

Let's talk about you bhai tuhje pata rhena chaiye tu sher hai out there build karte jaa it's in you second doubt shit sochna nahi hai abb. we are out here playground apna hai we have lot of plans now Joh hum char saal nahi kar paaye issi Zindagi mai pure karke jayenge. 

I know tere zindagi mai kuch lamhe aaise aaye the jaha pe tu mujhe dhund raha tha but mai tha nahi vaha uske liye dil se bhai maaf karde mujhe kyuki Phir hoyunga judaa Haan yeh vaada raha. A lot of success to you and I am here to celebrate it with you every time remember this no escape here Bhai.
Bhai love you <3

text:
Alan Bhai!

Cult-man of Y17 CSE. Your drams performance were really awesome. Dramatics was the only club whose performance I watched frequently (because of Varun and Nipun). You managed drams activities and department simultaneously, and it is no less than an inspiration.

Our first collaboration was obviously in TA201. Saath me kaafi bakchodi karte the :P fir bhi project kisi tarah nikal liya. But I still feel really sad ki our "Floating Ram Mandir" idea got rejected, atleast pehla Ram Mandir banta humara. Fir we frequently contacted in CS640, wrote a term paper and did a decent presentation in the limited time frame. I will always remember you as a hardworking, smart and phenomenal time-management person -- you know how to perform with limited time. I am sure you will do great in life. All the best!
author: Abhyuday  Pandey

text:

You are the CS gawd of IITK Y17. Your knowledge about systems is unparalleled. Department me patta bhi tumse puchhke hilta tha. Whenever I had many things to be done at same time, I always took inspiration from you. First year me you did CFD, GSoC and extra course together. Fir 1st year me internship and 3rd year me toh 3 internships together _/\_. I never expected you'll be joining a PhD. Infact, shayad last person I would have thought. I am sure you will do phenomenally well in life! You are humble, intelligent and ambitious. I wish we collaborate on some project at least once in future ...

author: Aishwarya  Agrawal

text:
oyy yaarr... chalo naa.... Bas yahi aata hai Rochak Dindor ke baare me socho to yahi sabse pehle yaad aata hai. Hands down the most fun person I knew in campus. Kitna bhi kharaab mood ho kitni bhi serious baat ho Rochak Dindor can take any topic and make it about chal maal maarte hai bc.
Although Aasman Gir Raha Hai me saath me the lekin I got to know the real Dindor during the brief practice of NSS nukkad. Kaala chasma lagae full swag me TS karta hua, itna ziddi ki nukkad khatam hone ke baad bhi apna 4-liner bol ke hi gaya.
Iske baad tumse dosti hui Summer me, Jab Aayush Ostwal was the Prop manager aur hum dono unke atyacharo se pareshaan hoke usko gariyate the aur in the end lad ke hi sahi kaam kar lete the. Also how can I forget Rochak DIndor the bad cop..... The most fun guy turned into a bad cop kyoki usi me to asli fun hai. Kedia se inspire hoke wo bachho ki maari thi ki hum dono bilkul opposite reasons se drameve-1 me bachon ke beech popular ho gaye the. 
Abhi thodi der pehle KT ke memoir me tune likha tha ki Varun ka Sarcasm Aishwarya se kam hai.... honoured but I have a similar comparison to make...... Nana kitni bhi koshish karle Rochak ki bakchodi kabhi match nahi kar paega. 
Saale tum msgs ke end me alvida to likh rahe ho lekin jaan lo ki tum officer ban jao chahe Pradhan Matri sutta lene tumhe hi phone karenge hum. Aur naa tumhe bhoolne denge kyoki jo scenes specially 2nd year Antaragni me apan milke banae the uske baad we are crime mates forever.
Bhai bauhat kuch hai tere baare me kehne ko to lekin ....... ab man nahi hai! Aapki shayari aur Ostwal ke liye innovative innovative gaaliyan sunne ka bada man karta hai..
Badalna mat be aur maa mat chudana kabhi milne ko bole to.. 
Baaki to Dindori baba zindabad hai the aur rahenge. Har Har Mahadev
author: Aishwarya  Agrawal

text:

Lekin chahe kuch bhi ho, InterIIT ya Chitkara tum humesha saath tha. Nukkad me research karna ho ya tumhara actually research portfolio ho, it was beyond what we guys could ever do.

text:
To : cheems@iitk.ac.in

Subject : Tum aache ho aur bahut bade Madarchod bhi 

Dear Harshit,
It was a very good time of around 3 years which we had spent together.Tu nahi hota toh the fun quotient of the  wing would have dropped significantly. I remember the first sem ka Harshit jo rota rehta tha and since then there was no looking back uske baad toh bas daase aur pranks aur masti hi hai to look forward. I hope ab tu kabhi bhi life mai flight tickets bina destination dekhe nahi bharega. My most proudest moment of IITK is still jab maine samu aur bandar ke saath milke teri cycle upar pahucha di thi. Also thanks verma boi for teaching me and samu ESC201 5 minutes before quiz and yes teri treat pending mai next jab milte toh dunga . Yaad hai kaise humne  sabko Atop pe pahucha diya tha and apan dono A206 aur A204 le liye the. 
Last sem was fun. Those among us nights, poker nights, Frisbee nights ;),  that Upmanyu ka show jaha apan sab gif mai convert ho gae the . Last but not the least the parties jaha # kanuumerikanuu #Tpkobulao and #AkshatMadarchod famous hue the . I still don't know maine kya kiya tha to deserve that. I have our paths cross again. 


Till that P**ma Lmao

Thank You,
Dota

Sirf tu hi hai, jispe memoir mai keval first year ke experience ke basis pe hi likh sakta hun. Mujhe yaad hai first year Orientation me when you introduced yourself to me. "Oyon" Bannerjee (you were my first exposure to Bengali accent - I was like dude why is talking like that).

text:
Einstein, Alan Watts and Bodhidharma rolled up into one hippie nigga.

Milte hain this/next year with more stories, and a wider variety of molecules.

text: Waise to we are from the same city, but we came here as acquaintances. We got into a petty fight and then one walk changed everything. I have got many defining moments from being with you and learnt a lot about life. You broaden my perspective. I have had 21 birthdays till now, but no one did anything special compared to what you did, you made me feel special that day with your excellent craft skills. Delhi ki wo trip humesha yaad rhegi, but the best time would undoubtedly be the time we spent in Mumbai. I hope you remember the horse ride. But above the big things in life, I value the small things we had, especially the painting of minions which I had to complete as you were not that good a painter. And also, the little notes you used to leave for me at unexpected places. It was a new experience for me to be in a relationship and I realised that it was the thing that was missing because I got you, you completed my life in the campus. Fire department ke saath waala incidence to main kabhi nhi bhulunga, aur na hi marine drive pe wo baithna, jaha aisa laga ki waqt ruk hi jaata to achha hota. Kaafi competitive spirit hai tujhme jo lifelong maintain rakhna hai (in a healthy way *wink*). We spent a lot of time in many different places. Kabhi RM, kabhi library, kabhi GH, but the best was the skywalk, and a close second is the Earth Science building. Wo road bhi achhi hai jo library se RM tak jaati hai. I respect you for the progress you have made since the first year. Poori journey kaafi achhi rahi but I still wish we had met earlier and got more time in the campus. Call me when you want, call me when you need. text:
Bc fir se likhna pdhegaü§¶‚Äç‚ôÄÔ∏è. Hope so tune wo grp m bheja hua nhi pdha hoga.
Shuru krti hu. 
Dost tum mc ho. Dost tum kuch jyada hi mc ho. Lekin ..lekin ..lekin... hme priy ho. Hmari aur palak ki local guardian(to be precise- mommmmmyyy) hone ka kirdar bakhoobi nibahaya h. 
Bc kya ho tum. Bt deti bhi ho bt m sambhalti bhi ho. Yrr jo bhi kaho m aaj tak tere se jitna jayada naraz  rhi hu utna hi tere se lipat kr royi hu wo bhi dhang se, fir wo chahe election results wali raat ho ya first year m meri fb id se khilwaad wali baat. Teri bhut si harkate nhi psnd mjhe..pr chill h ...every person comes with a package of goods and bads. Tumme dono cheeze extreme lgti hmeüòÇ.
Hum jaante dost tmhare liye hm shyd itne important nhi pr tum ho hmare liye. Waise to hme hmesa se ye baat pta thi..Lekin last  din tune proper realise krwa diya. Dukh hua tha hme. Lekin fir socha ki dost k kandho m bhut logo ko sambhalne ka bhaar h hum aur bhoja nhi bnte .....pr bc bura lga tha kaafi mc bc bhosdiki. BC dil ki feelings nikal gyiü§¶‚Äç‚ôÄÔ∏è. Lets change the topic.
Baaiten to kya hi yaad kre bhut h din raat subah shaam ird gird hi thi tum. Lab m fraud marrna, assignment  jugaadna, exam m dil khol kr cheating krana, aur kabhi kabhi uss chakkar m khud ko chudwa lenaüòú( aur yha pr palak n apna smjhdaro wala kirdar nibhaya aur  tjhe line pr laaya), class k liye uthana, nashta room m bhijwana, 710 wali se mere liye lad jana,  kya kya ginau..as i said ird gird tum hi thi dost( bc room bhi bagal m hi). Tere ko pta Teri wajah se daaru resist kr jaati thi m..pr mn h ki maanta nhiüòú( bevdi nhi hu pr m). 
Aur kya hi bole bhut kuch h tum bhi jaanti ho hm bhi jaante h. Lekin haan tumdono ki wajah se hmara bhi jeevan sudhra h. Bus aise hi saath deti rhna, galtiyon pr gariyati rhna( pr bc kabhi kabhi jayada ho jaata hüòí). Ek dukh hme tum hme kuch jyada hi underestimate krti ho dost. Itne nikkamme bhi nhi h hmüò¢ Sudhar rhi hu with time. Bc iss memoir m kuch jyada hi senty ho gyi m. Kya h tu. Dil se nikal rhi baatein sch m. Lets control.

Dost ek baat bolna chahenge ..Karma m thoda believe kia kro be. Iss concept ki abhi tk to tmne dhajjiyan hi uda rkhi h.

Baki pyaari to nhi tum dost pr dil k kaafi kareeb ho warna aise apne uss time k  sathi sangi ko chhor kr tmse nhi lipat kr nhi rote. Tmse to proper jhagda bhi kr liye dost aur aadhe ghnte k andar sort bhiüòÇ Yha m kuch insano ki baatein nhi krna chahungi warna ye memoir size aur bada ho jayega aur palak bhi kood jayegiüòÇ.

Ho gya mera..khne k liye bhut kuch h pr kuch baatien dil m rkhni pdti h(warna ye memoire visible krna layak nhi bachega).  
Ab jao maa chudao dost.

author: Anchal  Singh

text:
Lamba aur depressing memoir  h to man ho to pdhna warna hmesa ki tarah side kr dena ya unseen chhor dena..aadat to h hi mjhe iski bhi.

Hmmm...adhyay to khatam ho gya..m wapis kholna bhi nhi chahungi aisa adhyay na tere saath na kisi k saath. Teri kuch aur chahto k chakkar m m chud gyi. Mne shi bola tha ..we were a mismatch..a blunder. Pta nhi khne to bhut kuch chahti hu  pr ab to tere se mn ki baat krne m bhi apna chutiya katwana sa lg rha h. Already kat hi chuka h. M teri poem ka crux kuch sateek aur shi shabdo m batati hu. Ek ladka tha...campus m aaya bakchodi chhadi thi hr cheez try krne ka josh chada tha. Ek ladki dikhi thoda attract hua..aur yha bhi bakchoi chadi ki bolunga..to bol diya, ladki bhi attracted thi, usne haan bol diya. Fir whi kuch time baad bakchodi ki ichha khatam hui.. lga maja nhi aa rha..chahte kuch aur hui...socha the end kro. 
Tere memoir m sbne Teri  'will power' ki tareef ki h . M bhi krungi..aur m jo bol rhi thi tjhe last day call pr ki tune efforts nhi maare...ab smjh aaya ki tune efforts maarna chaaha hi nhi. Pta h m chutiya shi m hu. Mjhe bhi dikh rha tha ki apun k beech m kuch shi nhi h...aur ye m last winters ki baat nhi kr rhi...kaafi smay se lg rha tha.. kaafi gussa aata tha tere pr..pr sch m jab bhi tjhe dekhti thi to sb chala jata tha..gussane k mn nhi krta tha tere pr ki sb bolkr apne mn ki bhadas nikalu..aur sch m dil se try krti thi ki solution nikalu aur tere saath rhu..kyunki chahti hi tere saath rhna chahe jitna pareshani ho rhne m. Khte na agar insan se pyaar hota to saath rhne m taqleef bhi ho tb bhi rhte h. Shyd yhi kr rhi thi m. Jab tjhse aakr ant shant sawal puchti thi..aur tu bolta tha kaha kaha se seekh kr aa rhi kya faltu sawal puch rhi....m sch m seekh kr aur soch kr aati thi ki ye baat krungi..kyunki apne beech m conversation hi nhi hoti thi to try kr rhi thi ki thoda open ho apun dono, conversation initiate krne ki koshish krti thi. Introvert m bhi hu..isiliye tere liye extrovert bnne ki koshish krti thi. Anyways m ye sb krti thi kyunki tu meri priority tha. Bc ye likhne m bhi ab apne upar gussa aa rhi ki kyu tha priority tu jab m teri priority kabhi nhi thi. Relationship khatam hona h ye hmesa accepted tha. Abhi bhi iss baat ka dukh nhi h mjhe ki breakup hua. Bc galti kr di thi proposal accept krke..atleast ab teri life ka hissa to hoti formal hi shi. Tu meri college life ka most beutiful part h..lekin worst bhi h.. tjhe yaad rkhna chahti bhi hu aur nhi bhi. Tere pr gussa bhi h aur pyaar bhi. I hate that i love you. Ye bhi ek gaan ki line h. Lekin maa chudao yrr tum. Tmhe kabhi ye lga hi nhi apne side se to tere liye to aansbu bahana bhi ab chutiya katwane jaisa lgta. Tera ramya k liye jo meoir tha uski ek line pdh kr bhut dukh hua..(ki life k har stage m saath rhna) ..aisi hi kuch thi line. Pdh kr laga tha ki kaash mere liye bhi tu same feel krta. Pr whi baat tune kaata mne katwaya. Aage kabhi kisi se dil lgane m bhi drr lgega. Ho hi gya h abhi hi..bhale hi saath nhi rhti ab lekin jitna khule dil se dramatics walo se connect krti m Apne aap ko kisi aur se nhi rkti ab, bhale hi all time rhu unke saath. Waise ye achha hi h. Aise chutiyon ki tarah hr kisi se itna connect ho jaungi to zindagibhar roti hi reh jaungi. 
Tune jo reasons uss din CCD m diye the .sb chutiyap tha..schhai tune poem m likhi h..(chahte kuch aur)..yhi h sch.  Ab direct koi muh pr thodi bolega ki ho gya, ab mn nhi mera, maja nhi aara realtionship m, the end krte...kuch to cover krne k liye bolna hi hoga.  
M ye socha krti thi hemsa ki breakup hoga tb bhi contact m rhenge aur apni life k different mauko pr update krte rhenge. Pr bc m ye to dhyaan hi nhi di ki abhi relationship m to tu update krne m interest leta nhi h ..baad m lauda krega. Aur ye ichha abhi bhi h...pr at rhe same time nhi bhi h. Mn krta jaise tune mjhe for granted le rkha tha waise m bhi teri hr ek memory fek du. 'Stay away' khne ki mjhe jroort nhi kyunki wo to tu hmesa se tha. Bus i just want to hate you. Kyunki jaisa tu reason de rha tha na ki mjhe ignore krne m tjhe better feel ho rha tha..problem se bhaag kr. Same abhi mjhe lg rha. Tere ko hate krne m shyd m better move on kr paungi. Aur m kr bhi gyi thi kaafi hdd tk..bus campus aa kr alag sachhai smjh aayi. Abhi tk utopia m thi. Lgta tha ki nhi ye bhi mere liye feel kr rha tha. Aur aunty ki wajah se soch soch kr sb aisa kr rha. Pr ab dikha ki nhi ise kabhi interst nhi tha bus chala rha tha sb. Tune bola tha ki tu feel krta but mere jitna nhi... pr last day wo bhi dikh gya ki kitna krta. Priority list m kaha thi m teri wo bhi dikh gya. Mne kabhi top priority expect bhi nhi kri thi tere se ..bus chahiye tha ki atleast 5th 6th number pr rhu. Bus yhi expectation aaj tk dukh de rhi. Bc maa chudao kyu kru m tmhare liye dukh. Aayush ostwal tum deserve nhi krte itna. Phle doubt tha ki shyd m nhi desrve kr rhi thi itna ki m tere liye itni importnat bnu. Sch m deserve nhi krte tum. Pta h breakup k baad mjhe self-doubt ho gya tha ki m shyd tmjhe sambhal nhi paayi, apna relationship sambhal nhi paayi. Ye lgne lga tha ki shyd kabhi kisi ko nhi sambhal paaungi kyuki mjhe aata hi nhi sambhalna. Hmesa relatinship k mamle m fail ho jaungi. Lga rha tha ki tjhe smjh nhi paayi..waise baat to shi h smjh to m nhi paayi hu kyunki apunn baat hi kaha krte the. Tere ko jab jab mna kiya h na mne kisi cheez k liye milne aane se room aane se,  kyunki tb gussa rhta tha mere mn m tere pr ki tu nhi effort maarrha. Bus room m milne chale jao to hi baith loge baat Kr loge. Galtiyaan meri bhi thi bhut. Jab tjhe lga ki mai rhu saath m tb tb mai mostly nhi rhi hu. Bus isi wajah se lgta ki nhi smbhal skti shyd m kisi ko. Abe m bhut kuch batana chahti hu bolna chahti hu...bus isiliye last day tere se milna chaah rhi thi..ek baar tere kandhe m sir rkh kr rona chaah rhi thi tere ko hug krna chaah rhi thi. Apne mn ki saari baat bolna chaah rhi thi.. tb gussa nhi tha tere pr pr batana bhut kuch tha. Pr last din sch m chutiya kaata h yrr..tu bimar tha janti hu. Pr whi h teri ichha hoti na to tu jroor milta(since teri will power ki sb daad dete h). Anyhow milta. Pr whi h jab kabhi moh hi nhi tha itna to kyu miloge, kyu efforts maaroge ..maarna hi nhi chahoge.
