text:
Hello Jain! Kaisa hai bhai? 
Humaari kismet mai dost bnna to humesha se hi tha yar. First year mai terse jaada baat to ho nhi paai lekin humaare path first sem mai hi intersect hogye the. Maine tujhe sbse pehle notice kia tha Sociology mai, us din jb AKSharma mid sem ki copy dikhara tha aur tere shayad one of the highest the 22.5/ 23 ya aise hi kuch aur tu mere bagal mai answersheet pakad kr chill baitha tha. Aur mai page palat palatke totalling krra tha ki kahi no. to nhi galat added hai üòÇ üòÇ
Next encounter hua TA101 lab mai jb tu mere peeche waali table pe draw kia krta tha. Har week hum jaate the lab mai, mai humesha late. Pencil drafter se same vhi lines, circles bnate rehte the. Mera to bhut dimaag kharab hota tha yar usme aur mera humesha bekaar hi bnta tha üòÇ üòÇ üòÇ. Phr jaise jaise thoda steps bdne lage figures ke, mai kbhi kbhi terse puchta tha ki bhai kaise krna hai. Yhi tk tha humaara shayad first year mai mujhe jitna yaad hai üòÇ 
Humaara first decent interaction hua second year ke orientation mai. Thank God for that bro. Really. Thank God ki maine SG ke lie apply kia and because of laziness or other stupid reason, I didn‚Äôt miss either the form deadline or the interview. Because us orientation mai mujhe bhut maza bhi aaya and humaara interaction bhi hua. I am very grateful for that bro. I don‚Äôt exactly remember ki humaari baat kaise start hui but by the end of those 7 days, we became good mates. Being in the same branch and that too, such a heavy branch gave us the chance to further solidify our bond üòÇ 
Mujhe vo moment yaad hai bro jb maine pehli baar apne dimaag mai tujhe as a friend recognise kia. It was a day after the orientation of second year, jb humari classes ko start hue 5 7 din hogye the. Baarish hui thi us din and jameen puri geeli thi, shaam ka time tha, overcast weather. Mai shayad koi evening class se hall aara tha, on foot. Hume bata hi dia tha P. Singh ne ki notes roj padne hai (more on that later though ;P)Maine hall 3 gate se enter kia and tu left side se apni cycle pe aaraha tha kahi jaane ke lie. Phir tune modne ke lie brake maara aage ka (phutiya!) and tu cycle se phisal gya. Phir maine kuch kaha along the lines of, ‚Äú are bhai bhai bhai‚Äù and tu utha jameen se cycle leke. Maine pucha terse, ‚ÄúAur bhai notes pd lie kya is hafte ke?‚Äù Tune kaha, ‚Äúnahi yar abhi nhi. Kahi jaara hu, aake padunga.‚Äù Maine tujhe kaha, ‚ÄúAre bhai pdlo yar, aise kaise chalega‚Äù‚Ä¶‚Ä¶.  And then you rode off to somewhere. That‚Äôs the moment mujhe aisa feel hua ki I just talked to a friend of mine. 
Ab vo P.Singh waali baat üòÇ Yaad hai jb at the start of second year Kushlam and P.Singh ne guidance ke lie saare Hall 3 MTH Y17 ko gather kia tha reading room mai.  P.Singh ne kaha tha ki logic mai thodi mehnat krni padegi but Linear Algebra to chill hai üòÇ üòÇ üòÇ. Bhai us din humme se kisine ye nhi socha tha ki Linear Algebra ko kitna underestimate kia jaa raha tha aur uske aane waale mahino mai kya consequences honge. But jo bhi kaho bhai, we were the only ones from the hall who didn‚Äôt drop the course. Bhai hum warriors the dono üòÇ üòÇ I am really sorry ki tera D laga bro, sahi mai. SSS ne padaya bhi bhut ghatiya tha and grading to usse ghatiya ki thi. Khair, on another note mujhe aaj tk ye smjh main hi aaya ki tune vo course drop kaise nhi kia. I mean sbne line se drop kr dia tha, you and I were the only ones left. Pr uska faayda to hua, kuch ko to uske baad 2 baar aur lena pada course pass hone ke lie üòÇ üòÇ
Fourth sem to aur bhi khatarnaak tha yar. With Abstract Algebra and the Harry Potter Prof lol. Mujhe yaad hai abstract algebra mai kaisi mari rehti thi humaari. Hum kitne masoom the yar jo Linear Algebra ko tough samajhte the üòÇ Chalo shi hai tune drop krke 6th sem mai kr lia and aadhe sem mai hi baat khatam hogyi due to corona. Yakeen nhi hota but finally now every such course is in the past.
Sorry yar linear mai maine terko padaya nhi, agar mai thoda help krta to tera shaayd C lag jaata. I was selfish aur meri bhi bhut mari hui thi mid sem ke baad se. 
Second year mai initially humaari satti community academically kitni deniya haalat mai thi yar üòÇ. But towards the end of it, jo hum sabne apna group bnaya usse to humari performances hi better hogyi yar. Usi bahane humaari 4 saal ki degree bhi kaafi acche performance ke saath gujar gyi. Our dosti got further cemented aur humaara itna accha friend circle bhi bn gya. Humaara satti group me sb bnde itne mast jo hai yar. 
Vo har mth ke paper se pehle, library mai 1 table pe saath baith kr assignment krna, kbhi Santhanam ke, kbhi complex ke, kbhi stochastic ke, ek doosre ke doubts clear krna bhut yaad aaegaa yar. Us time hamari sbki phatti to rehti thi ki 1  ghante baad paper hai lekin un times pe hum sbse jaada close the and we were all helping each other through. Bhai mai bhut lucky tha jo mujhe ye group mil gya sahi mai.
And phr pandemic ke time, Zoom meetings krna for IME, time series and so on, itna maja aata tha yar shi mai. CE bhi krlia hum dono se saath, 1 term paper bhi bana lia saathüòÇ Bhai tu group mai tha to bhut help hogyi, tune model bna hi dia tha prediction ka. I guess OLA intern ne kaafi sikhaya tujhe and placement bhi accha lag gya. I am very happy for you, bro!
Bhai time to time tu gayab ho jaata tha and used to miss classes for days üòÇ üòÇ Kabhi for galaxy, kbhi photography, kbhi ritambra. Phr jb bhi tu  kabhi mess ya quad mai milta tha mai yhi kehta tha ki bhai class aa jaaya kr, pdlia kr and all. Us time maine kabhi tujhse kaha nhi but I had great respect for you and whatever you were pursuing from time to time. I think it was awesome ki tune college mai Ritaambra bhi manage kia, Galaxy mai hall ko lead bhi kia and photography bhi mst tareeke se ki and baaki bhi bhut saari cheeze ki jo mujhe yaad nhi hai ab. But us time, mai ye na kehkar tujhe kehta tha ki class aajaya kr taaki tu padai pe bhi thoda focus kre. Khair dheere dheere mujhe chamak hi gya tha ki kuch bhi hojaae, kitni bhi classes miss ho jaae, tu sahi grades le hi aata tha üòÇ Chaapu Jain!!!
Bhai tere saath jo parties attend kri, bhale hi few thi but they were worthwhile. Jb hum saath parties mai jaate the, bhut majaa aata tha. Jaise Shrotriya‚Äôs 18th birthday in CCD, the BBQ party, the pizza party in Urban Clave and the party in Hall 10 canteen. Kaafi maja aaya yar un outings mai shi mai. Party ke time aisa lagta tha jaise humari saari college problems thode time ke lie pause ho jaaati thi. Parties humesha bhut refreshing rahi yar. 
Terse lockdown ke shuru ke kuch mahine jaada baat to nhi hui yar, lekin phr you called me in August when the whole placement scenario started to unfold. Mujhe yaad hai, mai aise hi bahar road pe ghumra tha shaam ko and tera call aagya. Us din humne placement ke baare mai discuss kia and I think us hi din maine tujhe kaha bhi tha ki bhai I am not sure ki mujhe baithna hai ki nhi placement mai. But like many other times, tune kaafi samjhaya mujhe and kaafi guide bhi kia towards the resources to prepare for placements. Tune mujhe shayad mid august mai call kia tha bhai and tb jaake maine na chaahte hue preparation start ki üòÇ üòÇShi mai, agar tu call nhi krta to mai shayad September mai start krta preparationsüòÇ üòÇ
Chalo bhai at the end sb accha hogya, tu place bhi hogya mst company mai and merko clarity aagyi ek dum ki kya krna hai life mai.  Ek baar mujhe yaad hai ki tune call krke mujhe bola tha ki bhai kya faayda 15 lac per annum kamake jb Bilawar mai cousins/ dost apni dukaano se hi isse jaada kama lete hai. Bhai maine us baare mai kbhi jaada socha nhi but now that I think of it, it‚Äôs obvious ki 15 lac is beginning and corporate mai renumeration bhut hi jaada high hone tk increment hota rahega, unlike dukaan ka turnover, jo kuch lucky year hogya tb bhi 18 20 lac hi reach krega. 
Tere skills bhi kaafi acche hai bro, tu grasp bhi kaafi jaldi kr leta hai cheeze and high pressure environment mai deliver bhi mst krta hai.  Ab corporate mai jaake tu further seekhega ya MBA jo bhi krega, you‚Äôll definitely rock the corporate world. Khud pe bharosa to tujhe humesha se tha hi, but kuch bhi hojaae aage bhi kabhi khud se bharosa mt chodna. Just believe in yourself and keep rocking. ( Ho sake to Parshad ke saath startup krna üòÇ üòÇ 2 5 paise invest krke mai bhi thoda ameer ho jaaunga üòÇ üòÇ )
Bhai jtna time humne college mai saath spend kia, mst raha. Pandemic ki wajah se thoda cut short hogya vrna hum in 1.5 saal mai kaafi aur parties krte aur kaafi last moment group studies in library bhi. Koi nhi ab jb milenge, tb mst party karenge phrse. 
Khub mehnat krna bro, jo chahiye vo achieve krna. I wish you great success, fulfilment, Bilawar kya pure Rajasthan mai richest hone jitna paisa, and everything you want in life.  
At last, thank you for everything bro. I am really grateful that our paths crossed, and we became friends. Stay healthy and happy bro. Take care!

P.S. 32eese and dimples aise hi flash krte rehna, mst lagte terpe.
author: Dhawal  Raturi

text:
Hello Shrotriya bhai! Kaise ho?

Bro 2nd year se jb tu MTH ke lectures mai Goel ke saath aas paas baithne laga, tbse tumse dosti hui. Us time laga to nhi tha but aakhir humne MTH ke courses pure kr hi lie. Humara jo satti waalo ka group ha, usme tum ek atthi ho and also sbse jaada serious the exams and quizzes ke lie humesha. Thank you for that bro because bhut baar mai pd nhi raha hota tha upcoming tests ke lie aur tu mujhe aake bolta tha bhai pdle, quiz hai agle hafte ya end sem hai agle hafte and that would make me prepare from an earlier date and perform better.  Intern time pe bhi tune mujhe kaafi baar motivate as well as guide kia tha.

Bhai tere saath MTH ke alawa kisi topic pe jaada discussion hua nhi kbhi but from the three years that we spent doing courses together, ye samajh aagya ki you are a mst insaan. Mai kbhi tha to nhi drams mai pr suna bhut ijjat hai tumhaari vaha. Bhai apna ye I-don‚Äôt-give-a-darn-about-what-you-think waala attitude kbhi mat chorna aur aise hi life mai fearless hoke aage bdna!!!

Thank you for all you have done for me bro. I am really grateful that our paths crossed in these four years and that we got the chance to become friends. You are a hard-working person and I wish you great success, fulfilment, and prosperity in life. Stay healthy and happy bro. Take care!

P.S. I still can‚Äôt believe you are graduating at 19 and started college at 15.

text:
Dipak Frickin‚Äô Mahajan!!! Bro, how are you doing? 
It was worthwhile to have you, Aditya and Shubham in the adjacent room in the freshman year. The memories that we made in that short time itself are priceless. I remember that time when a bunch of 3rd years from 2-Bot caught us so happy that they couldn‚Äôt bear it and took us to the lawn and asked me to sing and you to dance to it. I never told you, but I was terrified that night and the only reason I felt safe was that you were there with me and I thought, I have my friend by my side and whatever happens, we‚Äôll get through this together. Contrary to our apprehension, the night took a rather hilarious turn, and we got an anecdote to laugh our asses off for the rest of our lives. I remember those numerous nights, when you, Shubham and I used to get together and mess with anyone we could possibly find in the wing (mostly, Tamonud ‚Äì Sorry Tamonud!) and used to make so much noise that Aditya could never sleep. And I remember the night before the PHY103 midsem when we pulled a night out in CC and you helped me get through all the tutorials and notes so that I could pass the next day. And I did. 

I remember the few but glorious trips that we took to BBQ or malls to watch a movie. Also, the time you and Tamonud treated the whole wing there (We love you for it!). I remember the time we watched Avengers: Infinity War (me, you, Aditya and Tamonud) and had to walk kilometres afterwards to find a ride back to college (What a day it was!). 

I remember the times in the sophomore, junior and senior years when I called on you for advice and guidance and you never turned me away, and the times you watched out for me when I was crashing academically. I also remember the innumerable times you helped me find greater clarity about my life and the times you saw me through my various never-ending crises and ever-recurring crossroads. 
I thank you for every one of these times. Thank you for being by my side, thank you for taking the time, thank you for every one of your advice, thank you for all the fun times, thank you for everything. 

Lastly, may I add how breath-taking it was to have had the chance to watch you grow and become this fabulous individual that you have become. That stooped, awkward kid that walked uneasily through the gates of Hall 03 in July 2017, inconfident, is now this confident, mature and more-learned-than-ever leader that is walking out head held high with a blazing charisma, having touched and enriched hundreds of lives, including mine. The way that you have lived these four years, fully and joyfully, inspires me and will continue to inspire me throughout my life. It is an honour to know you and have you as my bhai. I was very lucky that our paths crossed and I, whole-heartedly and unconditionally, wish you the best in life. May you be a thousand times more successful than anyone who has ever lived, and may you rise to your full potential, because you are INFINITE my friend. You are a fricking star, so please be and stay that way¬†forever.
author: Dhawal  Raturi

text:
Hello Naveen bhai! Kaise hai? 

Bhai humaari sbse pehle baat Takneek ke time hui thi jb hum dono astronomy mai gye the. Bhai kya mst din the yar vo. Raat raat ko hume Jaydev and Airan astronomy padate rehte the aur kai baar hum OAT ki cht pe constellations yad krte rehte the. Bhai kitne constellation yaad hogye the yar humme us time üòÇ üòÇ aur phr Atoms to Astronomy mai to alag hi maja aaya tha bhai. Humne kya khatarnaak chaapa tha. Second aae hum. Doosre halls ke Y16s aae ko harake Hum 2 Y17 ‚ÄòPI‚Äô team waale üòÇ üòÇ jeete. Bhai mst din tha yar. Phr uske baad jo astronomy club ke andar competition tha usme mai, tu aur Shrey gye the 1 team mai. Hum itna aage chal rahe the shuru mai bhai. Us 3rd year ne humaare saath accha nhi kia yar. Koi nhi bhai, jo hua so hua. Sbse acchi baat jo hui vo thi ki hum itne jaada acche dost bn gye us time se. 

 Phr second year se hum same branch mai hone ki wajah se laafi milte rehte the, baatein hoti rehti thi. Yaad hai second year ke starting mai P Singh ne Hall 3 MTH waalo ko reading room mai bulaya tha. Bhai kya advice dia tha unhoneüòÇüòÇ logic mai thoda mehnat lagegi baaki Linear Algebra to chill hai. Us time hme kya pata tha ki kitna underestimate kr dia hai humne MTH201 koüòÇüòÇ Aur fir fourth sem to aur bhi jordaar tha bhai, with abstract algebra and real analysis. Mujhe yakeen nhi hota bhai ki humne ye saare tough courses aakhir kaar paar kr lie and ab hume kuch time mai degree milne waali hai. 

Bhai hum classes mai to milte hi rehte the, kai baar mess mai aur quad mai bhi milte the. Jb milte the, khub hasi majak hota tha bhaiüòÇüòÇ Yaar humne jo saath mai pal bitae hai na, vo humesha yaad rahenge bhai. Kya mst the yar ye 4 saal. Maja hi aagya bhai.
Last mai phr se tujhe naukri lagne ke lie congratulate krna chahunga bhai. Jb mujhe pata chala teri job lg gyi, bhut accha laga bhai. I am very happy for you. Bhai mera gaana Fast Life itne baar stream krne ke lie bhut bhut dhanyawaad üòÇ üòÇ. Aage ab to mai kai gaane nikalunga, Fast Life se bhi acche nikalunga bro taaki tera aur accha manoranjan ho. 

Bhai I respect you a lot ki tune Takneek ke baad Astronomy nhi choda and college ke end tk pursue kia apne passion ko. Tu bhut hi jaada mst bnda hai. I am very grateful and lucky ki hum in 4 saal mai dost bne and ek doosre se mile. Bhai kbhi change mt hona, humesha aise hi chill rehna and life enjoy krna. Smile krna humesha, tere face pe bhut jchti hai bhai. 

I wish you great success, prosperity and fulfilment in life bhai, meri ye kaamna hai ki tu khub aage jaae life mai. Call krte rahenge bro, baat krte rahenge jb tk agli baar nhi milte. Aur jb milenge to pehle ki hi tarah hasi majak hoga. 
Take care bro. Stay happy and healthy. 
Till next timeüëãüëãüëã

text:
Hello Parshad bhai! Kya haal hai?
First year mai to jaada interaction nhi hua but jb MTH ne hum sb MTH waalo ki collectively leni shuru ki, it brought us closer, and we formed this awesome satti-guys-waala group, and it has helped us get through the MTH courses so successfully. Over time, you became one of the more serious and consistent persons in our group and all of us started looking to you during our academically intense times. 

Bro, the notes that you wrote on your iPad by attending every class, every day, helped us more in our courses than the professors themselves. Thanks to your notes, we got through all the exams and the quizzes almost smoothly üòú üòú üòú. Every time that I was suffering academically (because of my own deeds), I always knew I could fall back on you and your notes. At times, it must have frustrated you that I used to miss classes and then ask for your notes and help constantly but you never shied away from helping me. I don‚Äôt know if I even deserved to be treated in such a great way by you.  During the Internship season also, I came to you for advice and guidance a few times and you never turned me away. Thank you for being so well-informed and helpful all the time. In my 3rd and 4th year, when I was having trouble committing to academics, your dedication inspired me and motivated me to try and work harder. 

You are a genuinely great person bro. I enjoyed the few parties that we attended together, like Shrotriya‚Äôs 18th birthday in CCD (I can't believe that kid is graduating at 19!), the BBQ party, the pizza party in Urban Clave and the party in Hall 10 canteen.I think the video-editing that you do as freelancing is so over-the-top cool. It has enabled you to buy stuff for yourself, including that wicked CPU that you showed us one time in the group chat. You inspire me everyday to work harder on my dreams and also, to not wait on them but to work every day to achieve them.  

Thank you for all you have done for me. I am really grateful that our paths crossed in these four years and that we got the chance to become friends. You are a hard-working person and I wish you great success, fulfilment, and prosperity in life. Stay healthy and happy bro. Take care!

P.S. It‚Äôs just my gut feeling but I think you‚Äôd do great in the business world. I know that you have similar plans for yourself already and I think you‚Äôll be very successful. 
P.P.S. If I ever make some ‚Äòbig money' , it‚Äôs your start-up/business I‚Äôd want to invest it in.
author: Dhawal  Raturi

text:
Hello Arya! Kaisa hai bhai?
Humaara sbse pehla interaction hua tha, at the start of second year jb Kushlam and P.Singh ne guidance ke lie saare Hall 3 MTH Y17 ko gather kia tha reading room mai.  Yaad hai jb  P.Singh ne kaha tha ki logic mai thodi mehnat krni padegi but Linear Algebra to chill hai üòÇ üòÇ üòÇ. Bhai us din humme se kisine ye nhi socha tha ki humne Linear Algebra ko kitna underestimate kia hai aur uske aane waale mahino mai kya consequences honge. Aur phr fourth sem to aur bhi khatarnaak. With Abstract Algebra and the Harry Potter Prof lol. Mujhe yaad hai Abstract algebra mai kaisi mari rehti thi humaari. Hum kitne masoom the yar jo Linear Algebra ko tough samajhte the üòÇ Koi nhi. Ab every such course that we did is in the past.
Second year mai humaari satti community academically bhut miserable haalat mai thi yar. But towards the end of it, jo hum sabne forces jode and we became like Allied Powers, uski vajah se humaari 4 saal ki degree kaafi acche performance se saath gujar gyi. Iski vajah se humaari  dosti bhi acchi hogyi aur humaara itna accha friend circle bhi bn gya. Humaara satti group me sb bnde itne mast jo hai yar. 
Vo har mth ke paper se pehle, library mai 1 table pe saath baith kr assignment krna, kbhi Santhanam ke, kbhi complex ke, kbhi stochastic ke, ek doosre ke doubts clear krna bhut yaad aaegaa yar. Us time hamari sbki phatti to rehti thi ki 1  ghante baad paper hai lekin un times pe hum sbse jaada close the and we were all helping each other through. Bhai mai bhut lucky tha jo mujhe ye group mil gya sahi mai. 

Bhai kaafi baar mai MTH ko lekar kaafi pareshan rehta tha yar, lekin jb bhi tujhse baat krta tha, kaafi accha lagta tha. Tu humesha console krta  tha ki bhai pd le, assignment kr lenge saath mai, ho jaaega. 3rd and 4th year, when I was having trouble committing to acads, tb bhi tune kaafi help ki yar. 
Specially bhai in Time Series. Bhai us din tune group project mai bacha lia bs, thank you so much for that. Mai bhut careless tha yar, merko aakhri din yaad aaya ki group bhi dhunda hai aur project bhi bnana hai. Bhai mujhe yaad hai, 12 bje project submission ki deadline thi aur maine tujhe raat 8 bje call kia tha ki apne group mai rakh le. 
Bhai mujhe yakeen nhi hota ki tune itni aasani se mujhe include kr lia group mai. Mujhe aaj tk samajh nhi aata ki tune mujhe apne group mai add kyu kia, even after I asked you on the last day jb tum log project bna chuke the and maine itni kaamchori ki thi ki mai 1 group bhi nhi dhund paaya tha. But bhai thank you so much yar. Really. 
You are a genuinely good person bro. I am so grateful that we became friends. Jb hum saath parties mai jaate the, bhut majaa aata tha. Jaise Shrotriya‚Äôs 18th birthday in CCD, the BBQ party, the pizza party in Urban Clave and the party in Hall 10 canteen. Jitna time humne college mai saath spend kia, mst raha. Pandemic ki wajah se thoda cut short hogya vrna hum in 1.5 saal mai kaafi aur parties krte aur kaafi last moment group studies in library bhi. Koi nhi ab jb milenge, tb mst party karenge phrse. 
Bhai, I think you will do great in your career. Vaise bhi humaare group mai, applied maths mai sbse accha tu hi perform krta hai, ye maine Prob Stats se hi observe kr lia tha. Bhai finance mai tujhe interest hai, bhut rise krega tu and bhut jaada paisa kamaega. Khub mehnat krna bro, jo chahiye vo achieve krna. I wish you great success, fulfilment, South Bombay mai 1 ghar, and everything you want in life.  
At last, thank you for everything bro. I am really grateful that our paths crossed in these four years and that we became friends. Stay healthy and happy bro. Take care!

P.S. Tu bhut smart hai bhai, maintain rakhna humesha khudko. Tond mt aane dena!!!
author: Dhawal  Raturi

text:
Hello Shrey bhai! Kaisa hai yar??

Bhai humaari aise regularly kbhi baat nhi hui but jb bhi tu milta tha bhut accha lagta tha yar. Humne 4 saal mai kaja mile waha hasi majaak kia.

Tu bhai 12th ke beech mai Maths mai switch krke IIT aaya, bhai I salute you for it and I am always in awe jb merko ye yaad aati hai ki tu jee mai 700 rank laaya tha ye sb krke bhi. Bhai is baat mai koi shk nhi ki tu chaapu hai, tha aur rahega. Bhai tera physics mai itna interest tha ki tune uske lie Medical se IIT mai apna aim switch kr lia. Tera PhD and research ka man hai, jaroor krna bhai. Ab dual degree mai mst mehnat krna bhai. Bhai mujhe yakeen hai ki tu aage jaake bhut successful hoga life mai. Bhale hi abhi aisa exactly obvious na lgra ho, aur terko pichle 2 3 saal ki performance se thoda inconfident feel hora ho but bhai tu apne pe bharosa krna kbhi mt chodna yar. You just keep going bro. Stephen Hawkings ka bachlors performance kaafi ghatiya tha bhai and he is one of the most remarkable physicists till date. Bhai tune apni life physics ko dedicate krne ki sochi hai,  jaroor krna bhai.

Bhai tu HSS ka bhut hi integral part raha since the first year, in fact you led HSS. Bhai Hindi ke prati jo tera passion hai usko humesha kaayam rakhna and humesha creativity apni engage rehna. Apne creative talent ko waste mt jaane dena please. Mujhe aisa lgta hai ki HSS ne tujhe ek platform dia in 4 years mai which helped you create your identlity, your confidence and your overall personality. Bhai usne tujhe family dee hai. Us family ko bacha ke rakhna bhai and HSS ne jo tujhme aisi aag jalai hai usse kbhi bujhne mt dena. 

Life mai kai baar tu akela hoga and ek dusre se itna contact na hora ho kya pata but apni self worth kbhi mt bhulna bro. Tu heera hai, heera heera hi rehta hai, dhul lag jaae to koila nhi bn jaaeta. Keep gong on your path bhai, mujhe pata hai ki tujhe in 4 saalo mai bhut baar aisa laga ki tera jo physics ka interest tha vo tu kisi prof ko convey jada acche se nhi kr paaya and you couldn‚Äôt find exactly the support you wanted for Physics but koi nhi bhai lage rehna and I am sure you‚Äôll find it eventually. Abhi naa shi to PhD mai.

Bhai tu bhut hi shi bnda hai and I love you. Bhai tera sleep cycle yaad krke and jokes vgera yaad krke mai jindagi bhar hasa krungaüòÇüòÇüòÇ. Fourth year mai jo hume 50 days ke lie college vaaps aane ka mauka mila usme hum 3 4 baar mile, mujhe bhut accha laga bhai I am very grateful and lucky bro ki in 4 saalo mai merko tera dost bnne ka mauka mila. 

Tu kbhi doosre kya sochenge, irrespective of that humesha apna asli opinion bolta hai and I respect you for that bro. Kbhi change mt hona bro, aise hi chill rehna always!  Mess mai humaara saath meal krna humesha yaad aaega bhai. Hum dono ka connection bhut hi mst tha shuru se!

Baaki I wish you great success, prosperity and fulfilment in life bhai, meri ye kaamna hai ki tu khub aage jaae life mai aur apna full potential achieve kre. 

Take care bro. Stay happy and healthy. 

Till next timeüëãüëãüëã
author: Dhawal  Raturi

text:
Hello Ujjwal bhai! Kaise ho?

Humaari sabse pehle baat hui thi jb hum freshers inferno mai Hall 3 ke lie basketball khele the saath. Aur uske baad to CPA mai milna hota rehta tha. 

Pr tumhe acche se jaanne ka mauka to Summer Camp mai hi mila aur hum kaafi acche dost bhi bn gye. Bhai summer camp mere in 4 saalo mai sbse best time tha and you were one of the reasons for it. Summer camp ka time yaad krta hu to aisa lagta hai jaise camp koi sapna tha, kyunki hum us time bs khate, khelte aur soya krte the. Court se thakkr aate the aur jb so nhi rahe hote the to hasi majak chalta rehta tha. Vo time bhut mst tha yar aur jo humaari team thi vo bhi sb mst bnde the. 2nd year ke Udhgosh se maine basketball khelna chor dia tha but dost to humesha hi rahenge. 

Uske baad bhi kaafi baar mulakaat aur baatein hoti rahi. 2nd year mai saath SG bhi rahe aur hall mai kbhi kbhi mess ya quad mai milte rehte the. Ek shaam quad mai 3 bot ke saamne baithke humne dher saari baatein bhi ki thi sur apni problems bhi share ki thi ek doosre se. OAT mai saath milkar, basketball team ko humne birthday treat bhi krai thi. To mulakaate to bhut hui pr kaafi nhi ho paai kbhi pandemic ki vajah se, pr jitni bhi hui, uske lie mai bhut grateful hu bro. 

Tumne basketball 3rd year ke end tk continue rakha and actually you were the only one from our batch to do so. I have huge respect for you because of that. You were always deeply dedicated to everything you committed to, from studies to basketball. That's why I'm sure you'll do great in life and will rise to your maximum potential. 

Thank you for all the experiences we had bhai. It has been so much fun to know you. You are a genuinely good person. Also you are one of those very few people I've met, that think about life in long-term. Always take advantage of that. Terse baat krke humesha accha lagta tha because you used to listen so patiently and genuinely. I will miss you a lot brother. I wish you all the success in the world bhai. May you find your purpose and have a fulfilled and prosperous life. Stay healthy and happy. Take care bhai. I'll stay in touch. 

P.S. PhD aur research krne ka sapna kabhi mt chorna bro. Bhale hi due to pandemic, situation thodi tough hogyi hai but never give up on your dreams, ever.

text:
Agar bhagwan khud bhi aake bolega ki SHAILABH jaisi RANDI kahi aur mil sakti hai to bhi nahi maanunga. Randi Rone ki definition hai bhai tu, ye kabhi mat bhuliyo, na hi badaliyo. Yahan sabse closest friends me se ek. Sabse kanjoos, harami aur jugaadu logo me se bhi ek. Par dependable aur Hai dil ka boht acha.
Shailabh Ji ki jai!!!!
Yaad to hoga hi jab teri vajeh se purana cooler thik kara ke puri summer chud gayi thi hamari ü§£. 3 saal se gym jane ki baat kari par gaya kabhi nahi. Wing ka ML gawd, paper pe paper publish karata rehta hai, abhi covid ke baad last 2 mahine bhi aaye to mostly paper ki zoom meetings me hi busy, Phir bhi extreme randi rona ki yaar "mujhse bada chutiya duniya me ho nahi sakta" - Ye sahi bhi hai aur galat bhi. 
Bithoor trip to yaad hogi vo lambi cycle ride aur boat rowing. Tere saath wali Manali trip sabse memorable cheezon me se ek hai mere liye bhai, saari hikings aur adventure sports, tere wall climbing skills bhi (inspired from CSE profs).
Ye covid wale last ke mahino me campus puri raat ghume, cards khele, khaya piya aur jam ke maze kare humne, last me long drive to Delhi bhi.
Adobe ML me pure campus me akela selection hone ke baad bhi aur upar jane ki teri bhookh yaad rahegi, neutron star milgaya par black hole ki bhookh.
Research me to tu aur upar jayega hi ye sabko pata hai.
Bas ye dukh hai ki ab mulakaat kam hogiü•∫.

text:
CRINGE ALERT!!
It started with scaring other couples on the skywalk and ended with, NO, it never ended :). You can never imagine how much you meant to me at the time we met. You still have no idea how precious those late-night walks were, how beautiful the sun looked at 5 am with you, how you just understood what I meant, how you just knew what to say at every fucking time, how you always kept my priorities at top, how you never really complained about anything, how you made me laugh even if it wasn‚Äôt necessary. I know everything you did required patience and dedication, I know it wasn‚Äôt easy for you to get out of your comfort zone but there wasn‚Äôt even one single time when you backed out. You are the most rational boyfriend one could expect. Even when we were fighting, you were there for me. Many of the things can not be written here but I know you'll always feel them while reading this. I do and always will appreciate those little things, our walks on "footpaths" both inside and outside campus, our first date in bazooka, sneaking through moti jheel barricades, the gatecrash in Kanpur, binging tv series, our spot(wink) and infinite other things. I know I can get too competitive and sometimes it can be difficult but you never uttered a word. I am extremely happy for us to have crossed many challenges that came in our relationship. It was as close to ideal as WE could get. We had our quirks and weirdness. I like having really conversations with you, I love sharing the "we could go to jail for this" humor with you. I love that you typed my pet name exactly 69 times in my memoir. I love a million things about you and I can fill pages but can not. You'll know them. I just want to say one thing, there may be a thousand ways in which a relationship MAY or may NOT go, but I know we'll choose what will work best for us. LOVE YOU MOTU üñ§

PS:  Even if we decide to break up, I REALLY hope our friendship stays this magical. :)
author: Gunjan  Jalori

text:
A youngster was attending a video conference with his Manager who was upset over the background noises. The Youngster turned around and told his grandmother to keep quiet.

She walked towards the youngster, to take a look into what he was doing and saw a person on the Monitor and asked, ‚ÄúWho is he?‚Äù

The youngster muted his audio and video and said, ‚ÄúHe is my Manager‚Äù.

She said, ‚ÄúI want to talk to your Manager‚Äù. But the youngster denied. By the time the Manager started pinging the youngster and the youngster unmuted to talk and his grandmother shouted, ‚ÄúManager I want to talk to you".

The Manager agreed and the youngster unmuted the video. The grandmother, with a smile said, ‚ÄúNamaste‚Äù and introduced herself and the Manager also greeted her.

She said, ‚ÄúYou look upset‚Äù.

The Manager said, ‚ÄúYeah, some kind of work tension, a lot of noise around your house and we are not able to complete the meeting in time‚Äù.

The Grand Mother asked, ‚ÄúMay I help solve your problem?‚Äù

Her grandson was stopping her and telling her to keep quiet.

The Manager said, ‚ÄúIt‚Äôs ok, let her speak‚Äù.

The Grandmother narrated, ‚ÄúOnce there was a Young man, who sat under a tree for taking rest. He was continuously hearing a bird‚Äôs sound. He lifted his head and seeing a bird, started chasing it, so that he could peacefully take some rest. The bird came closer to him and said, ‚ÄúYou are taking rest under my nest. I will not ask you to leave this place but you should learn to co-exist with us‚Äù.

The Grandmother looked at both of them and said, ‚ÄúYour Home is your nest‚Äù where you are supposed to take rest and bond with your dear and near ones. I do understand the Covid-19 situation, but you should also understand that our home is not your office.

When we come to visit our family members at your office place, we are expected to behave professionally or maintain a certain decorum.

Similarly, when you are using our home for your office work, you should understand the situation at our home.

There is nothing wrong with working from home, but remember, it is the family members benevolent nature, that is keeping the corporate world functioning today and the economy running.

She looked at the manager and asked, ‚ÄúAm I correct ?‚Äù

The Manager‚Äôs mother peeped and said "You are absolutely right‚Äù.
author: Harish  Dechiraju

text:
There are several things to consider before buying a product that contains the label ‚ÄúMade in China‚Äù.

Every purchase of a ‚ÄúMade in China‚Äù product directly supports the Chinese Communist Party (CCP). The corporate income tax rate is 15%-25% [1]. The CCP levies taxes on businesses which it uses to boost the power and influence the party possesses both in China and abroad. There was once the belief that China would become more democratic as it traded with the world. This prediction has never occurred. In fact, the CCP is stronger than ever before.

The Chinese Communist Party runs hundreds of concentration camps across the country, and your purchase of Chinese made products allow these abuses to continue. At the time of this writing, China has at least 1 million Muslim Uighurs in Chinese run concentration camps [2] where murder, rape, and torture are common occurrences [3]. There are also reports that describe how Chinese authorities are forcing minority women to undergo sterilization [4]. And these abuses detailed above are not just happening to Muslims. Christians, Buddhists, and the Kazakh are also imprisoned in these concentration camps [5] [6]. Women in the camps who do not sing patriotic communist songs or praise president Xi Jinping are raped and electrocuted repeatedly [7].

China suppresses freedom of expression. Communist authorities routinely detain, persecute, and jail people for crimes such as ‚Äúspreading rumors‚Äù and ‚Äúinsulting the countries leaders‚Äù, according to Human Rights Watch [8] and Amnesty International [9].

China allowed the so-called ‚ÄúCOVID-19‚Äù virus to proliferate in its own borders before it became a pandemic. When Dr. Li Wenliang, the ‚ÄúWuhan Whistleblower‚Äù, alerted his community that a strange new virus was killing people, Chinese Communist authorities jailed him where he subsequently died from COVID-19 in jail [10]. The CCP then censored all information about the virus. Eventually, it jumped the border and became a worldwide pandemic.

text:
Firstly, Biotech/BSBE is NOT Biology. It is a proper engineering field with ample math, coding and physics involved.
BSBE at IITK is a wonderful place to be at, 
however I must correct you its very different from the curriculum of 'biotech' at IITD or IITR.
BSBE here will, in your four years, give you a good insight into a variety of fields in the given branch - Microbiology, Biochemistry, Biotechnology, Biochemical Engineering, Neurobiology, Computational Bio, Biophysics. In addition to this, its a highly practical field with a lot of application based approach.
The best part is the huge growing sector of BSBE in the world and its intersection with all the branches that exist today.
Take any branch name and add biology next to it - you will get a highly demanding field of biotechnology which is very lucrative in terms of research.
Example - Computational Bio and Neuroscience; Bioelectricity; Biochem engg; Biophysics; Biochemistry; Biomaterials...
Also, I can assure that irrespective of a persons former background, they can ace these subjects easily and go on for masters in any of the intersections in the future.
Hectic: No
Opportunities : Infinite, not in corporate jobs, but research oriented fields.
Money : Really good, once a person has done specialisation/masters, and is sincere enough.
#thatsiitk

text:
This is an extroverts view on the world and on the "problem" that introverts cause.

To me? You all talk too much, you waste words and time. You're a distraction to what actually matters and more often than not you're detracting from the world, not adding to it with your insightful conversations.

Now I don't blame you for it, I don't think me better. But I do not want to talk to you, I do not need to talk to you. I enjoy myself more without the empty words being exchanged. My extrovert partner? We have comfortable silences with entire conversations taking places with looks, squeezes of the hand, and facial expressions.

Something you consider awkward might not feel that way to me, while your natural flowing conversation feels forced. If I wanted to share something with you I would, but honestly I probably wouldn't find it often necessary and when I did it's not some word shattering revelation it simply something I found worth saying in the same way you find all the words you use worth saying.

No more important, no less.

It feels like you find the silence awkward and blame that awkwardness on the individual. When really they're likely comfortable with it and find the conversation awkward. If I wanted to talk to someone I would, it's not introversion that would stop me from having a conversation it would be anxiety and to me that's something else entirely.

text:
I have been programming (not "coding", how awfully, you kids these days, say) powerful DOS programs in assembly since 1999 and I don't know any of your hipster node.js bullshit that makes you look "cool". Seriously, get that shit outta here. You're just making yourself look like clowns typing some incomprehensible sugarified as fuck bullshit, half of which, in fact, is written by your brand new and shiny Electron-based text editor you enjoy every second of, and the other half of which, is copied from fucking StackOverflow. Look, we didn't even fucking have that and we did shit, and you suckers can't even spend a single second without it. You spend hours looking for a gorgeous and flawless color scheme for it so your so-called "coding" is always a pleasure for you. We didn't even fucking have IntelliSense or linters, you fucking spoiled little brats. Stop making programming look like a joke and go back to your parents' basements, where you are truly who you are.

Burn HTML. Burn CSS. Burn JavaScript. Burn PHP. Burn the fucking web.

I bet you won't even be able to fucking stand writing some C for an embedded system without crying to your mommy

... about how there are so fucking many compilers errors and everything went not as you expected.

You call C fucking unsafe? Look at JavaScript. Look at PHP. They let you pull out insane bullshit while you don't even notice. And then you spend hours trying to find out what you did wrong.

C is actually useful.

Everything you fucking see on your screen has atleast 60% of C or C++ in it.

Oh, what is JavaScript useful for? Rolling a stupid fucking dropdown menu or a sexy as fuck banner animation?

I know what you're thinking.

And by the way, CSS is fucking stupid.

It makes no sense half and a quarter of the time.

Web development is gross.

And you know it.

You try to compensate it by making dumb frameworks that require ages to load because they weigh over 16MiB for no fucking reason, but it is no use.

Oh, I wonder why none of you said anything yet.

Probably because I just roasted you all hard and you can't deny it.

text:
Hyo,
We spent a lot of moments together, from the labs of Vishal to labs of Control, and then this pandemic struck. I initially got you as an irritating, hyperactive and over conscious type of person, but still it was fun being friend with you, I don‚Äôt know why, but somehow, I just managed to survive with you. xD xD
I will always miss those heated bullshit arguments that we used to have, which never reached a conclusion. Those poor jokes from you which can made anyone cry, bullying professors and those theories towards life.
Accha, for that imposter kaand, I literally do not know how I was involved, I can only say sorry for that because even I am not aware how those things got fired up. That incident, I guess ruined everything between us, but I am fine, if this is what makes u satisfied. That is what life is, you can have anything in life, but you cannot have everything that you want.
Nonetheless, it was fun being with you for almost like 2 years. If I will ever write a book on my college life, you will surely be a chapter in it, may be two :P. It finally goes this way, not how long, but how well you have lived, is the main thing, I am sure these two years are enough, if not further.
Baaki memories to bhut h, can‚Äôt write each one of them here :P.
Have a great future ahead.
Ciao

text:
Careful Jay. It's Ms Flamme here. 

Jab starting me aaya tha to itni entropy expect nhi ki tha. Silly me? Haan partly. College me aa rhe ho, how do you expect everything to go so nice n cheese, but spare me thoda sa, mai itna bhi guilty nhi because aane ke 2-3 din me hee ek ladki se milna hua. Vo mere bagal me hi baithi thi, sab theek tha, itne me hi vo achanak meri taraf mudi, aur ek shabd boli. Ek, sirf ek. Samajh to nhi paya mai us samay kya hua, kya ho gya. Samajh to aaj bhi nhi paya hu par us shabd ki uttejna usi pal se alag ho gyi zindagi bhar ke liye. Usne kajal lagaya tha, badi hi pyaari lag rhi thi vo.

Tujhe yaad hoga ki humne numbers exchange nhi kiye the bade time tak. Mudreka ke thru milte the, hawa ki philosophy discuss krte the. God ki existence ko brutally destroy aur defend kiya. Self ki depths ko, heights ko, beliefs ko, connects ko, sab kuch test hua, sab kuch test kiya. Discussions bohot hue. Aur in sab ke beech pata chala tu jitni thoughts me rebel hai, utni hi life me bhi.

Tu ye jaanti hogi Gunjan ki walks pe bohot saari mast crazy baate ki, par tu ye nhi jaanti hogi ki in walks ke pehle mai padh ke aata tha, prepare krke aata tha. Tujhe ye realisation hoga Gunjan ki teri company special to thi, par tu ye nhi jaanti hogi ki isse pehle kabhi itna tense nhi hua. Tu shayad is chij se bhi aware hogi Gunjan ki tere liye vo poem ek din me likhi thi, par tu ye nhi jaanti hogi ki us din ke baad mai aajtak koi poem complete nhi kar paya. Bohot attempts liye, abhi bhi ek pe kaam kr rha par yet koi complete nhi kr paya. 

2nd year me aaye, milna kam ho gya. Jaha hafte me roz milte the aur 2-3 baar ghumne chale jaate the, vaha ab dikhna bhi naseeb me nhi hua. Tu padhai me dhyan laga rhi thi, mai pata nhi kya kr rha tha. Time tha, time kam nhi pada par ye bhi sach hai ki hum nhi mile itna jitna pehle milte the.

Nhi socha tha ye gap badhta hi chala jayega. Beech beech me sparks the. Diro bungalow ke bahar us raat ki light setting imprinted hai man me, rhegi aur anant tak. Vo chaurahe ke aage road kinare mandir se emanating green light yaad hai? Tune hath pakad ke aur dara diya tha. Baate jab bhi hui tere sath, acchi hui. It's hard to find koi aur un baato ke liye. Kam hone lagi, par vo elements the. Vo glory thi. Shayad apne apne raaste pakad liye. Antaragni ho gyi, mere bahane khatam. Ek din room pe aya tere. Us din samajh aayi. Baat kr rhe the, teri aankhein nam ho gyi. Mujhe maaf krna Gunjan. I learnt life me kuch us din. Won't go down that fucking lane ever again. 

Mai kabhi concede nhi krna chahta, na krunga ki tu cute hai. Par ab samajh gya hu. Pehle mai delusional tha, ab denial me hu. Tu hai cute, aur nhi bhi. 

If there's a bond I care and value about so much in my life, it's with you. Abhi bhi waaqif nhi ise kya kehte hain, but the day it comes to it, I'll put up a good fight, take note of that! Hey, aisa ho skta hai ki kinhi moments me dikhe nahi, but stay there na, call me up, and ask me blunt up front. I'll take responsibility of rest. 

Listening to T wala song. You're the one, suit, for it. Ms Flamme, üíö
author: Jai Ranjan Sharma

author: Jay  Mundra

text: Broosdk If I go back in time now and agar tu bole tu batti club ke coordi ka form nahi bhar raha to mostly mein backout kar lun. It was one of the best things I did in campus of course and usko average se memorable banane mein I think tera sabse bada contri hoga. And I don‚Äôt remember koi chote chote incidents but this all is because we bonded right from day1. Baakiyon se dheere dheere bonding hui thi. I believe we were always on the same page which is very rare jab etne saare decisions lene ho. Apan mein 0 ladai hui hogi which is quite an achivement. Infact Abhigyan and tere saath bina koi topic ke bhulla kaatne mein bhi kitna maja aata tha. Election time tere liye to kaafi jyada stressful huva hoga but mere liye kaafi memorable tha. After winning Techmeet, my best moment on campus would be jab tu finally jeeta. And ofc ******* etna gussa aaya tha jab last day backout ki baat kar raha tha. Vo to stress mein dikh raha tha esliye kaafi bola nahi. So, overall I would say 3rd year shayad best year of campus life hoga and uska tu lkaafi bada part raha. Mil jaane be kabhi. Ab bhi mokka mile to Gurgaon ko prefer karna Mumbai jaakar kya karega. Vaise ab lag raha chote chote incidents bhi likh dene chayie the 10 saal baad mile to kuch yaad karne ke liye to hona chayie na xD.

text:
Meri pyaariii roomiieee, IITK behen and my cry-mate, we only had each other even in our 1st semester (usse fights bhi boht hote the - raat ko lights ke liye, room ki safai ke liye, proper talking and living etiquette ke liye!). 1st year tera notes na dena yaad rahega mujhe üòõ. Fir apni branch same ho gyi, batti club mein saath kaam kiye. Tune boht mehanat ki thi usme aur kitni saari ppts deni padi thi na (Uff!). IME mein kaam karne mein boht maze aaye par aur voh band bas tere hi haath pe fit aata tha (kha pi liya kar kuch aur moti ho jaa, mess mein saara khana waste kar deti thi!). I will miss those long late night talks we had about so many people and topics - especially about each other‚Äôs crushes and love life üòõ! Hume ek doosre ke itne saare secrets pta na! Meko kai baar rote hue sambhala hai tune. Thanks for bearing with my repeating same talks about the same personüòÉüòÉ! Meko taekwondo mein bhi toh tu hi leke gayi thi. Paper mein mere marks dekh ke aana, mera rebate fill karna and chappal almirah mein rakhne ke liye shukriya yaar! Apne TA ke group mein bhi boht bakwas ki apan ne - maze aaye. Fir truth‚Ä¶ waali cheez! Kya kya hua hai na apne saath - ek baar toh tera fb account hi hack ho gya tha! Do you remember our 1st solo trip to oxidation pond? Tree pe chadhke photoshoot karwayeüòÅüòÅ

Yaar 4 saal were really fun and it has been great being your friend‚ù§Ô∏è. You might seem a little selfish at start but that‚Äôs not true. You are a very emotional person who cares a lot about his friends‚Äô feelings. Thanks for taking care of me all this time.

Haan yaar call pe baat nhi ki na last year. Abhi future me - we will stay connected and share a ton of secretsüòÅ!

Itni khas kuch baat chit nhi hui us time lekin tumhare group ki bakchodi se ye to pata chal gaya tha ki launda chaapu to hai bhai. 2nd year me Takneek ke liye wing visits se leke Takneek jeetne tak ka safar bhai apan ne saath tay kiya hai. Teri wo takneek event me plane udane ki zidd sab yaad hai bhai. Bombay trip ki masti se leke Techkriti ke liye nighouts maarna aur wo tera Tashi ke saath judges se ladna aur phir Neeraj se behes karna bhai tu hamesha se hi honest raha hai bhai sabke saath aise hi rehna yaar. Phir yaar tum sabke support se mera Coordi banna thanks bhai is Kabil samajhne ke liye. Quad and Heli wale project me apan ka Flyer(tu) aur Builder(mai) duo bhai baccho se jyada tu excited rehta tha ki Quad ke liye bhai. Bhai wo tera FPV se stunts maarna mujhse bina puche aur bhai wo tere dangerous Flips. Bombay me quad event mere hagne ke baavajood tera chill attitude. Tera wo peeke ishq me rona saale band karde use yaad karna ab.

Bhai tera doston ke liye unconditional support aur tera never say die attitude mujhe sabse best lagta hai. Chahe kuch bhi ho jaye kabhi na stress lena aur bakiyon ko hamesha  motivate karte rehna kaise kar leta hai bhai. Aise hi rahiyo dost hamesha ekdum unfiltered. Corona khatam hote hi Club trip karte hai. Future me bhi chaapte rahiyo yhi dua hai. Aur ho sake to Gurgaon aa ja.
author: Kevlin

text:
‚ÄúWorkaholic, Selfless person and Extremely talented ‚Äù ye teen words mujhe lagta hai aapki personality ko aptly define karte hai aur party karne me aapse upar to koi nhi hai bhai. Aap aur Vedant hi mujhe aap bolte ho thanks Madhur itna respect dene ke liye. 

1st year ke robotricks waale event ke time se leke Takneek tak aapke under kaam karna bhai hamesha enjoy kara hai. Aapse accha leader nhi dekha bhai maine isiliye bolta tha ki SnT Gensec ban jaao aap maane hi nhi. SnT council me Prashant ko galliyane se leke Hall-12 ki mkb karne tak kitni memories banyi hai apan ne. MTH102 ke time aapka vector space padhana. Mere non-veg khane pe aapka meri moj lena üòÖ. Yaar pata hai Madhur aapke saath agar mai bhi Robo Club join kar leta to shayad mai bhi aapke jaisa chaapu ban jaata just kidding üòÖ. TA202 ke to kya hi khene jab apan ek dusre ko dekh ke haste rehte the bhai epic course gujra yaar wo. Aakhiri ke kuch dino me to bhai epic parties kari hai aur kismat se aapki maar ka shikaar mai nhi bana üòÖ. Trip ki bakchodiyan to alag level thi subah subah utkhe saath me wo iconic Sunrise dekhna. 

 
Jaldi se ek aur trip plan karo madhur sab normal hote hi kyunki itna bada kaam sirf aap hi kar sakte ho. Aise hi hamesha help karte rehna mujhe aur haan aapke 290 shares mere paas shi salamat hai chinta mat karo.
author: Kevlin

text:
Kaha se Suru karun Yugesh aapke saath to itni memories hai. Chalo kosis karta hun.

First day of college hum sabhi Hall 5 quad me wait kar rahe the Rooms ke liye tabhi aapki entry hoti hai aur aapko dekhte hi I was like ye to poster boy hai bhai Patna ka aur phir shaam me jab room me jaata hun to dekhta hun yhi banda mera roomie bhi hai bhai literally Triple Room ka gham compensate ho gaya tha. Abhi bhi yaad hai mujhe jab mera pehla phone aaya tha to aap kitne excited the. Mafia Nights se leke Late Night Oat sessions tak bhai kitni yaadein hai. Theatre me pehli movie (Murder on the Orient express) aapne hi dikhayi thi. Wo aapka Google Pay install karwanaüòÇ. ESC101 ke exam din aapki Binary Trees ki class, TA201 exam ke liye saath me ratta maarna. Aapka hamesha motivate karte rehna. Mujpe aapka unconditional trust thanks bhai meant a lot to me. Bhai aapka facebook post jab mai Coordinator bana tha thank you yaar for your unconditional love and affection. Aapke Saath duniya daari ke debates karna. 

Ab jaldi se sum up karta hun warna 2-3 page likh dunga. Intellectual level pe to Kabhi nhi connect kar paya lekin emotional level pe hamesha connect kiya. Aapka hamesha honest suggestion dena whether ki wo accha lage ya kharab aur over the time wo hamesha hi sahi nikalte the. Hamesha aise hi suggestions dete rehna Yugesh. Aap aao na aao mai jarur aa jaunga Switzerland milne.

Bade bhai ki tarah hamesha motivate karne ke liye thanks Rommie.

author: Nitish Vikas Deshpande

text:
Hi Madhur,

We knew each other through SnT council. I had heard a lot about you from Jay.  We interacted mostly in the SnT council meets in Senate Hall. I recall that you had participated in the Electrowiz competition conducted by Eclub in senate hall. Your team was among the top-performing teams (mostly because many of the questions that I had set were from our common EE courses). Although we didn't collaborate much over any project, it was fun to jointly organize many events for SnT council.  I wish that we would have collaborated more with the Robo club.

Besides SnT council, we did our EMEC lab of EE381 together. In 8th sem, we also did Prof. AKJ's estimation and detection course together. Our areas of interest may be quite different now. Hope that our paths may cross sometime in the future. All the best for your future endeavors.
author: Nitish Vikas Deshpande

text:
Hi Sandeep.  
Thanks for being a part of my IIT K journey.  I recall that we had first connected in the second year when we were allotted a common alumni buddy in the Alumni Buddy program. Although my alumni buddy did not connect with me, I am fortunate that I connected with you. 

We have completed numerous courses and course projects together for the last 1 year. I am fortunate that one of the term papers with you resulted in a publication [1] that was also our first conference paper.  You have influenced many of my decisions in the last year that helped me shape my academic interests and future plans.  I hope that our paths will cross again and we collaborate on some research problems at the intersection of our research interests.

All the best for your future endeavors.

[1]Spectral Efficiency in Poisson Cluster Based HetNets with Users-Basestations Correlation https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/9342826
author: Nitish Vikas Deshpande

text:
Hi Soumya, 

I am glad that I met you at IIT K in our second year.  We have been through several ups and downs together (especially third sem and fourth sem).  We connected first time through Eclub.  Remember the time when ERA was being founded. Most of our time together in second year was spent in Prof Behera's lab, EClub and later at Hall 12 ERA room / Suraj's room.

We had also collaborated in TIIDC. You had accompanied me in finding a faculty mentor the day before deadline. The funniest part of TIIDC was recording the video.  You have supported me in all of my crazy ventures. 

The one unique thing that you taught me was sending GIFs on Facebook messenger. Our chat is full of GIFs.

You really manage your time well. You took several leadership roles simultaneously in SnT council. You led several problem statements
author: Nitish Vikas Deshpande

text:
Hi Tarish,

You are among the one at IIT K whom I know the longest.  We know each other since class 8. We were together for the Young Scientist exam coaching class by Kotwal ma'am. After that, we joined Vidyalankar for Physics Olympiad classes.  Are you in touch with our mutual friends from Vidyalankar? 

You were the coordinator of the coolest club in SnT council. I remember the night that I spent in Astro club when collaborating for a SnT council proposal.
Thanks for allowing Eclub to conduct one of our secys meets at Astro club.
I wish that I could have spent more time at Astro Club.

It is great that you pursued your liking towards Physics and Astronomy at IIT K. I recall that you had medals in Astronomy Olympiads before joining college. Although I don't know much about astronomy, radio astronomy sounds cool as it has a bit of intersection with electrical engineering. I recall that you too, had collaborated with the Microwave lab in EE for one of your projects. 

Physics and electrical engineering have a good amount of intersection. Hopefully, our paths might cross again in the future.

If you are in Thane, we might meet up sometime.

All the best for your future endeavors.

text:
Aaj likhne ka kaafi mood bana hai, to thoda lamba or senti jaayega, padhke to tune khush hi hona hai madarchod, tu hi bolti hai naa jyada expressive nahi hu me, pehli or aakhiri baar express kr rhi, to khush ho jaana pdhke, iske baad nhi hone waala ye. One of the best things jo IITK ne mjhe diya hai wo tu hai (sounding like Nareda I know, but chill hai). Yaad hoga tjhe kaisi masoom si, bholi bhaali aayi thi me, mjhe jo itna frank kiya hai logo se, sikhaya ki dost duniya itni achi nhi hai jitni tum samajhti ho, duniya madarchod hai. Har ek cheez me mjhe support kiya, rules todhne sikhaye (sbse epic ESC201 tha), mere itne jyada saare randi rone sune har time, gaaliyan bhi di hai sunne ke baad, but har cheez ka solution nikal jaata tha yrr tjhse baat krke. Ek point tha meri har problem ka solution tu thi, fir ek point aaya (pata hi hoga kyu aaya), jab , meri sbse badi problem hi tu thi. Behenchod, agar kisi insaan ki wajah se me zindagi me kabhi royi hungi naa to wo tu hai. Behechod, bolti hai ki JD or tum ekdum similar ho, to ye nhi samajh aaya tjhe ki wo rota hai itna, to ho sakta hai me bhi roti hu. Mtlb me close nhi hoti logon se jyada, pata hi hai tjhe, but pata nhi terese hu. Wahan Shimla me literally meri feelings ye thi ki yaar sahi me bohot sahi tha pehle ki kisise bhi close nhi thi, kyuki end me to sbko chhodna hi hota hai, ye bhi chhod hi di naa (firse Nareda waali feel). But thike, mtlb mjhe pata hai me tere liye kaafi important hu, but bc banda aane ke baad sab badal jaate hai, tum bhi koi exception nhi thi. Or agar campus me mjhe sbse jyada nafrat ek insaan se hai to wo hai JD, but baat ye hai ki uski jyada koi glti nhi hai usme. Shimla waali trip bohot hi jyada bekaar thi, wahan pe pata nhi hoga 2 raat me bhi kaafi royi thi, but hamesha ki tarah tu thi nhi sambhalne ko, kyuki pati bhi tha naa tumhare paas to, or fir uske baad jab time bacha to tumne Karan ko pakad liya, jisse hume realise hua ki tumhare liye life me aage badhna or doosre log dhoondna bohot aasan hai (another instance jab tune abhi campus me kaha tha ki me nhi aa rhi hall, mjhe hall-9 me patte khelne me bohot majja aa rha hai), but JD or mere jaise logo ke liye nhi hai, yaad rakhna isse. Khair, dost shukriya humare jeevan me aane ke liye, humko sudharne ke liye, Tindal jaise logon ko judge krne me humari help krne ke liye, or hume humare ye upar likhe hue jaise faaltu ke randi rone sunke unko suljhaane ke liye. Me jaanti hu bohot saare logon ko campus me, but dil ka connect sirf tere saath hai, chuhiya, Thanya kisike saath nhi hai. Itni connected bachpan se aaj tak apne gharwaalo ke alawa shayad nhi hongi kisise bhi. Lekin behenchod isiliye connect nhi hoti me, kyuki fir uss insaan se related faaltu ki baaton pe bohot jyada sochne lag jaati hu me, or ye khaaali hone ka asar nhi hai agar tjhe wo lag raha hai to. Agar me bohot jyada hi busy hoti naa to bhi mjhe tere ye last 1 mahine ke ignorance se shayad utna hi farak padta. Bas bhadas thi nikaal di, feel mat krna jyada warna ro dogi. Achi insaan ho yrr tum, bas exclusice raho humare liye, sbke paas jaa jaake unki dikkatein naa suljhaya karo, I feel jealous (ye nhi btaya maine shayad tjhe kabhi pehle). PLease meri life se jaana mat kabhi bhi. Baaki to me nhi jaane dungi, bas JD ki baat aati hai to me fir piche ho jaati hu. Wahan tjhe hi sambhalna pdega. BC pdhte pdhte gaaliyan de rhi hogi ki ek rone waala kam tha kya jo isne bhi shuru kr diye, but thike mummy se nhi royenge to kisse royenge, or hum thodi roj roj rote hai. 

BC bas visible mat krna isko, acha sa gaaliyon bhara likhenge tumhara visible karane le liye.
author: Palak  Agrawal

text:
PR calling Festi!!
Yaar teri first memory naa 1st year ki hai, jab tu Katiyar ke liye birthday card banane GH ayaa tha, lol (Am I allowed to openly say this?). Hamesha ye discussion kaafi hota tha humara ki kaafi similar ho tum dono, literal bhai lagte ho. 
Anyway, uske baad Antaragni'19 ke baad ig diwali ke baad call aata hai tera, bro milna hai kuch gadbad ho gyi. BC bhand hoke chhoti ko bata diya tha tune, meri fati nhi thi, but jis tareeke se tu express kr rha tha, aisa lag rha tha ki fatni chahiye. Uske baad to yrr fir CORE TEAM, alag feels, alag expectations, or kaafi jyada enthu. Enthu to ussi se yaad aata hai jo "KAIROS" naam pe kitna jyada discussion hua tha, lol. But, ek point aane ke baad, enthu kaafi down ho gaya tha. Tune or Shrey ne hi milke sambhala tha poora, placements ke baad sbko jinda kiya, or fir karali BC (wo feel nhi hai, but apni Antargni thi yrr). Bohot jyada miss kiya maine, jo hall-12 me saath milke kaam or bakchodi ki hai tum logo ne (photos or videos aa rhi thi mere paas regularly), or jo final night bhand hue ho tum log. Goa trip jldi plan karo yrr, saath me bhand hona hai BC (OAT ki tarah nhi hopefully).  Dukh kaafi raehga on-ground Antaragni naa hone ka, jitna expected tha utni bond nhi ho paayi me team me, but at the end kya hi kar sakte hai.  Khair kaafi BT hai meri udhar, Tindal ke saamne nahi nikali kabhi, tere saamne pata nhi kyu nikal rhi. Anyways, umeed hai Goa me jld hi milenge. Tab tak Take Care, or apna enthu or feel humesha aisi hi rakhna!!
author: Palak  Agrawal

text:
Bohot Shimla Shimla ho raha tha, to aise randomly tera naam search kiya. Expected nhi tha ki tu hoga, or abhi bhi expected nhi hai ki tu ye padhega, but thike kuch kuch baatein kehni thi terese. 
Sabse pehle to uss din Delhi me mere saath ghoomne ke liye THANK YOU!! Uss science museum me kaafi majja aaya tha. Secondly as a person I like you a lot. Kaafi khulke baatein krta hai tu. Thirdly, mjhe jyada logon se touch me rehna nahi aata bilkul bhi, lekin terese icha hai pata nhi kyu touch me rehne ki, but bas samajh nhi aata baat kya karu. Isiliye jyada touch me nhi reh paati. But here is to hoping we may meet someday, somewhere. And all your dreams and fantasies about physics come true some day. Also, tu bohot awesome hai yrr!! Take Care!!

Yo Ratnesh!!
Yaar sabse pehle to sorry agar meri kisi bhi baat ka kabhi bura laga ho to, dil me kuch nhi hota yrr, bas nikal jaata hai kabhi kabhi pressure or frustation me. Baaki yaar kaafi dedicated or sincere insaan ho tum, or apni responsibilities kaafi ache se poori krte rhe ho hamesha se saari. Majja aaya tha saath kaam krke kaafi, bas ek photo miss ho gyi Antaragni ke time ki, memory rehti hamesha ki wo. Anyway, thanks for being such a supportive and hard-working co-manager. Fir milenge kabhi. All the very best for your future. Take Care!!
author: Palak  Agrawal

text:
Yaar samajh nhi aa rha kya hi likhu tere baare me, ajeeb sa praani hai tu bohot jyada, but dil ke bohot kareeb hai. Bohot jyada hi frequently baat nhi hoti terese, lekin pata rehta hai ki tu hai, or humesha rahega. Kyu hai, wo nhi pata bas, hehe. Gussa aaya tha terepe, jab maal jugaadne ko kaha tha tjhe, or naatak kr rha tha tu, but fir Apollo ke bahar jab reason bataya tha, tab bohot acha laga tha. Wo sunke laga B-115 me start me aake bhi faayda kuch nhi hota XD. Lekin ek baar to aaungi tere paas bhand hoke, tjhe disappoint krne ke liye. 
Purani yaadein to kya hi yaad krni, chhodo, pata hi hai tjhe sab. Baaki wo raakhi ka din yaad rahega mjhe humesha. Pehli baar tjhe legit bhand dekha tha, or gussa nhi aaya tha, kaafi achi harkatein ki thi tune uss din, kulfi khaake. Kaafi fun tha wo, tere mast se expressions, aaj bhi video dekhke majja aa jaata hai. 
Baaki mood swings bade khatarnak hai tere, or fattu to hai hi tu, ab to maan hi jaa. Bas BT padwaani aati hai tjhe, uske baad sambhalna bhi seekhle. 
Chalo UPSC nikalo fatafat, hum bhi faayda uthaye taaki bhai ke sarkari babu hone ka. Milte to rehna hi hai terese. Ache se padhai likhayi karo, or mera naam roshan karo. Take Care!!

‚ÄúJha2‚Äù...this is your name in my contact listüòÇ...just to respect youüòú...but you actually deserve it man‚Ä¶‚Äôchapu‚Äô is the most used lingo in iitk ig...people use it on almost everyday, chahe sala wo hag k hi kyo n aaya hoüòÉ...but you are the real ‚Äòchapu‚Äô man...mtlb everywhere‚Ä¶.chahe wo acads ho, chess ho, swimming ho, ya frisbee ho, and yes a poke champion...everywhere man...and itna kuchh krte hue bhi maintaining such a good acads recordüôè...You are such a nice person yar...We didn‚Äôt even talk during our 1st sem, if i‚Äôm correct...again due to hagga partition yar...but i wish ki hmari dosti 1st year se hoti (fir to 1st yr bhi waste kr dete FIFA me üòÉ)...do u remember?The first thing that we talked about was FIFAüòÜ...came to your room...bhai FIFA dal do yar mere dabbe meüòÉ...and waited in your room only, till i got it installed...us din se kya tha, nikal pda mai apne jindgi barbad krne k raho peüòÇ...and that day, i didn‚Äôt expect ki we will eventually become such a good friends...and yes i feel very very lucky that i got one of the nicest human being in my life...you are probably the first maharashtrian, who didn‚Äôt have negative thoughts about biharis,,even at the beginningü§£).  If we talk about the time spent together, kya hi bolu bc, hmesha to kuchh n kuchh krte hi rhta tha tu..always busy...bahut bol diye to sale khel leta tha fifa...but kya hi kr skte tum, dept bhi to gandu hi tha tumharaüòÖ...but still, we did bakchodi...bhar bhar k...played baddi together, and yes your favourite ‚Äòfrisbee‚Äô...initially, i thought ki frisbee is not at interesting at all...but when played, i actually enjoyed it a lot (aur to aur, this sports suits me, less injury possibleüôÇ)...so thank you for making me explore one more sports...you might be good at many things, but bro you need more and more practice in fifa. text:
‚ÄúJha2‚Äù...this is your name in my contact list(laugh emoji)...just to respect you(tongue out emoji)...but you actually deserve it man‚Ä¶‚Äôchapu‚Äô is the most used lingo in iitk ig...people use it on almost everyday, chahe sala wo hag k hi kyo n aaya ho(laugh emoji)...but you are the real ‚Äòchapu‚Äô man...mtlb everywhere‚Ä¶.chahe wo acads ho, chess ho, swimming ho, ya frisbee ho, and yes a poke champion...everywhere man...and itna kuchh krte hue bhi maintaining such a good acads record(pranam emoji)...You are such a nice person yar...We didn‚Äôt even talk during our 1st sem, if i‚Äôm correct...again due to hagga partition yar...but i wish ki hmari dosti 1st year se hoti (fir to 1st yr bhi waste kr dete FIFA me (laugh emoji))...do u remember?The first thing that we talked about was FIFA(laugh emoji)...came to your room...bhai FIFA dal do yar mere dabbe me(laugh emoji)...and waited in your room only, till i got it installed...us din se kya tha, nikal pda mai apne jindgi barbad krne k raho pe(laugh emoji)...and that day, i didn‚Äôt expect ki we will eventually become such a good friends...and yes i feel very very lucky that i got one of the nicest human being in my life...you are probably the first maharashtrian, who didn‚Äôt have negative thoughts about biharis,,even at the beginning(laugh emoji)).  If we talk about the time spent together, kya hi bolu bc, hmesha to kuchh n kuchh krte hi rhta tha tu..always busy...bahut bol diye to sale khel leta tha fifa...but kya hi kr skte tum, dept bhi to gandu hi tha tumhara(laugh emoji)...but still, we did bakchodi...bhar bhar k...played baddi together, and yes your favourite ‚Äòfrisbee‚Äô...initially, i thought ki frisbee is not at interesting at all...but when played, i actually enjoyed it a lot (aur to aur, this sports suits me, less injury possible(laugh emoji))...so thank you for making me explore one more sports...you might be good at many things, but bro you need more and more practice in fifa. Do you know why i used to call , particularly you to play fifa??to bring back the confidence(laugh emoji)...aur wo Rishikesh trip kafi badhiya tha yar...kafi mje kiye hmne...probably the best trip that we could ever make...it was really awesome. 
And, how could i forget that internship prep bro...you really helped me a lot...mtlb that is the time when i started coding, facing a lot of difficulties, but i had not to worry much cause you were there...also, there were a lot of time you helped me for which i will always be grateful to you. So, thank you so much for being the part of my life, and making my college time memorable. And sorry for not coming to Goa, but whenever you make another trip plan, consider me in. aur maine chess khelna start kr diya hai...just for fun...so jb bhi milo, thode tricks btate rhna...All the best for your future...andha paise kmao, aur mera trip sponsor krte rhna...Good luck. Love you(heart emoji) and take care!
author: Mukesh  Kumar

text:
Hi Pandey..hope u have moved on by now. I didn‚Äôt want to write anything about you after what you have doneüò†(those who know, know it), but tum dil k kafi achhe aadmi ho‚ù§Ô∏è. Also, I know that it was your last possible chance, so I forgive you. I can write a whole page on this topic..you know that...but i will maintain the dignity of memoir and epsilon amount of  your ijjat. 
We didn‚Äôt talk even once during our 1st year, cause you were maggu at that time...baat krne  k liye kha hi time tha tere pas...and at that time, mere ko ye bilkul ye nhi lga ki we will become such a good friend. From the time I know you, you were the most chillest person of our wing, and ofc Chapu. Do u remember, tumhare pas kafi stories hoti thi , and u needed someone to spill it out. And then you come to most vella guy of the wing, who had always time for others (ofc it was me). That was the time when we got along and the strength of our friendship increased, if u remember. I really enjoyed those stories man (just say thanks from my side to the main storyteller). do u remember, ek din mera laptop aur notebook sb le liye the..just bcz i was not ready to listen to your stories...agle subah quiz thi...b**k aise harkate mt kiya kro, nhi to koi suplex deke chala jayega.I know i hit u once, i‚Äôm really sorry for this...but kya mja aaya tha yar...aisa lga i‚Äôm in wwe ring, and i‚Äôm giving you superman punch. Even after this, we are such a good friend. But i have to ask you a question. Why you always betray me??chahe wo fluid mechanics ki endsem ho ya placement session ho...why??? jaise bhi ho bhai...but tum dil k kafi achhe ho...and it‚Äôs very difficult to find people with a good heart...mai khud ko kafi lucky manta hu ki i got friends like you...playing full night badminton and volleyball...wo bhi kya din the..i really miss those days yar...and yes we haven‚Äôt gone to any trip together, but next time be ready...to sponsor my trip!üòç(JPMC k itne paise ka kya krega). So, thank you for making my life at campus more beautiful and memorable bhai. There is a quote ‚ÄúHope for the best, but be prepared for the worst‚Äù. ‚ÄòWorst‚Äô to tumhare sath ho hi chuka hai, now its time for the best. So, All the best for your future ahead. Bhut paise kamao...Be Rich...Ambani is not that far!
P.S. - You deserve someone better!
author: Mukesh  Kumar

author: Mukesh  Kumar

text:
Hello Anshu (pet name revealed)..
Bhai, I just can‚Äôt imagine it‚Äôs been 7 years of friendship..and I wish ki it remains forever‚ù§Ô∏è. It is very difficult for any friendship to go so long. We both are very thankful to god that everything happened in our favour. I came to know you during our JEE preparations at FIITJEE. Initially I thought...ya, seems like a nice guy...started talking...and eventually became good friends while helping each other in solving fiitjee booklets. U remember anshu? that fight between us...MTH publication k book ko leke...i refused to give it to you, and u stopped talking to me...was kidding manüòÇ...and then we became very good friends. This made me realise ki with whoever i had a little nok jhok , they became very good friends of mine (kyo pandey aur piyush üòÇ). We got so lucky bhai‚Ä¶.same batch at FIITJEE, both repeated for JEE, again got in the same institute and batch(Parth Ranker ROCKS(rock emoji)), and fortunately got in the same college and even the same hall bhaiüíó...everything happened in favor of our friendship. And I feel very lucky that you are one of my friends, and trust me, you have a very special place in my lifeü§ó. I mean it needs a lot of effort to maintain any type of relationship, and I respect you a lot for all your efforts to keep our friendship going. 
This whole memoir would be like green trees but with no fruits if I don‚Äôt talk about our college life. You made these whole four years of college life really awesome by showing us your writing skill. Bhai mera SHAYAR..kasam se yar...kya likhte ho bhai..ekdum gaddar...I had only listend earlier ki ‚ÄúPYAR ME LOG SHAYAR BN JATE HAI‚Äù, but you made me believe it. Here is a two-liner that came in my mind spontaneously, hope u like it:
Ek tum aur tera adhoora pyar, i wish ki it happens bar bar;
You might not want it to happen again, but trust me, this will be the reason for your name and fame!
I just can‚Äôt wait to see you on youtube and your book to be a bestseller in India...macha dena bhai! 
And yes, thank you for being there whenever I needed someone. Whenever I was in a confusion for choosing or doing something or not, you were the first person who I went to. And, ofc how can we both forget that traumatic period of my lifeüò¢...man i just can‚Äôt tell how i would have been if u were not there. I am really really thankful to you bhai. And thanks to you for making me start all the nashe thingsüòú...it really feels amazing. Kuchh nashe bache hai, but i know ki tu uski bhi aadat lgwa dega. But, how could I forget that Nainital trip man. Bhai, mai maut ko takk se choo k wapas aa gya tha...it was scary..but i really enjoyed it man. The funniest trip was our regular Patna trip. Sutta fukna at every Patna trip. Jb bhi tum patna aate the, ek lambi list hoti thi tumhare pas, of all the street-food and their locations.Jha bhi jao, ‚Äòpaisa wasool‚Äô ki responsibility tum lete the. Bhai, to ek din bhukha aata tha, paisa wasool krne k liye. and ghar jakar pta chlta tha ki you have gained 5 kgs of weight...i mean are you for real??? And itne khane wale bnde ko achanak se diet follow krna, i can‚Äôt believe my eyes. Jo bhi ho, you are following it strictly, and yes huge respect for this. Aur bhai, wo 85 kg wali bet ko jyada serious mt le yar, gareeb aadmi ko jeene nhi doge kyaüòÇ. The most hilarious and memorable trip to Patna was of course Jan‚Äô21. First of all, you should thank me for making you lose your weights, and saving your auto ka kirayaüòú. We did so much kand bhai...you know that! 
Last but not the least, I wish you very very good luck for your great journey ahead. I hope you fulfill all your dreams, and most importantly follow your diet, cause the ‚ÄòBET‚Äô is still ON.
Love you 3000xüíìüíì
P.S.- tujhe kya, phatna hoga to phat jaunga;
	Apne baap ka khata hu, nikal warna yhi utha k patak dunga!

text:
Yaar pizza hut wali baat bolke tune purani  haseen yaade yaad dila di. Memoirs likhte waqt mai sake sath bitaye hue 4 saal ko revisit kar rha hu tere sath bhi wahi karunga..bas wo aakhri samay thoda bigad gya apna jiska mujhe zindagi bhar khed rahega..but lets not ruin the special moments we had just bcoz of that lil bump. Toh shuru karte hai Revisit:
yaad hai mujhe sabse pehle tu kaise mila tha.. mai , tushar aur aanshul apne room me the tab tu aur ip(saanp) aaya aur tum dono aake bade ajeeb tarike se baat kiye humse. Actually ajeeb tab laga q ki tab bohot gaaliya deke baat kar rhe the tum logüòÇüòÇ abhi yaad karta hu toh lagta hai normal toh thaüòÇüòÇ. Apan ek sath freshers mein dance kiye lekin tab nhi jaante the... asli janne lage jab 2nd year start hua tab. tere room me aana jaana start hua. jab bhi aata tha sota rehta tha aur darr k uth jaata tha. Aur fir bolta tha "areee yaar mai so gya padhna tha mujheü§£ü§£". wo bhi kya din the. Asli maza tab aana start hua jab avi tu aur mai milke chize karna start kar diye. jaise bahar jaana . bakchodi karna., piza hut toh bhai bhai yaad hi rahega. Roshan se bhi mila tere karan. Aur wo tere birthday wali raat bhai maza aa gya tha. bancho meri lene lag gye the sabüòÅüòÅ. bhai wo plane banani wali lab jisme jaate the ..tu kaam kart tha aur hum kitne bakchodi karte the. kitne din exam k pehle sath me padheüòâ(ghanta padhe). Mirzapur sath me dekha tha jisme sadke patli patli thiü§£ü§£.     Baaki sab badhiya tha yaar bas last mein thodi chize bigad gyi..lekin mujhe pata hai q hui ... hall change nhi hona chahiye tha yaar. same hall mein rehte na toh mast hota. baaki yaar mai yahi boulnga ki wo time bhool jaao.  Tere sath trip pe jaana reh hi gya..koi nhi meri job lagte hi jayenge aur tu bhi IAS ban jayega tab tak. fir foreign ki trip karengeüòçüòç. tu toh mujhe har baar yaad karega jab "ba ko va pronunce karegaü§£ü§£" Baaki yahi bolunga thanks bhai.. in 4 saalo me anginat lamhe sath mein bitaye and mai hamesha yaad karunke khush hounga (last me 1-2 assu bhi niklenge but khushi kü•∫) . milte hai jald hi.

text:
Yaar vakul ab kya likhu mein. Tu ek aisa banda hai jiske sath mujhe lagta hai memories kam bani. Abhi jab apan bichad gye to mai sochta hu ki yaar kaash aur time sath mein hota aur time chahiye tha apna sath mein. Past mein jaake mai sochta hu toh mujhe samaz aaya ki aisa q hua. Jab tu, tushar aur anshul k sath rehne laga tab mai dance mein busy tha aur apna time sync nhi ho paaya. Kaash tu thoda pehle aaataüò≠üò≠...kaash. Par chalo ab jo bhi memories hai use hi yaad karte hai. Manali trip toh puri college life mein sabse badhiya chiz thi. Aur waha hi tere sath pehli baar kch genuine yaade baniüòÇüòÇ. Kitne maze kiye yaar trip pe, kaash ek aur trip ho jaatiüò•.....kaash. Trip pe tu hamesha udaas rehta tha tu qki tujhe lagta tha ki ulti ho jayegiü§£ü§£.  jab Kunal ultiya karne laga tab tu fence k bahar jaake khada ho gya wo kitna funny thaü§£ü§£. Fir tu mai aur baba ek hi tent mein soye the. Aur maza aaya tha jab paragliding k liye jaa rhe the tab mai tujhe bol rha tha ki mai bhi nhi karunga toh tu bolne laga ki haan apan dono nhi karenge. lekin baadme kar hi liya sabneüòÇ. Chalo Trip kahatm hui. Ab baat karte hai aakhri 2 mahine jo sath mein the. Yaar time kitne jaldi nikal gya. Kaash aur time milta sath mein.....kaaash. Wo time best tha yaar jo bhi mila hame sath mein tum teeno k sath jo bhi maze kiye maza aagya. Bhalehi tum logo ne mere bina bhi maze kar liye bohot lekin kya karta padhna bhi thana mujhe toh mai hamesha sath nhi reh paayaüò•(mai hamesha regret karunga ye baat). Ek din pehle jo show chalaya tune wo bhi mujhe yaad rahegaüòÇ. Tujhe high dekh k maine bhi socha hai ki jab job lag jayegi tab mai bhi apna show chalaunga ek baar tohüòÇ.  
Aakhri mein yahi kahunga ki regret toh hai par khushi bhi hai ki kam hi sahi bohot achha time spend kiya tere sath. Dance video bhi toh banna hai.üòÇ...I will miss you my boiiü•∞ü•∞.
