text:
Nipun 'Acting' Goyal... ye naam jo apan ne last last me soche the, 4 saal ka poora apna poora character baya kar dete hai. Ye kaafi sahi cheez hai.

Tera ek moment yaad karke likhte likhte hasi arahi bhaii üòÇü§£. Varun ke room pe apan saare baithe hai, tu gadar phunka hua hai, ramya aur kt idhar serious BT suna rahe aur tu ek taraf to unki baat sunke rota hai, to dusri taraf bc insta pe memes padhke hasta haiüòÇ, ohh bhai kya gajab scene tha wo. Pehli baar dhang se bhand hua tere kamre me, socha maja aayega but DJ khalid ban gaya. Bc tu to chalta firta comedy show hai, aspass rahe to haste hasate hi rehta hai.

Apni pehli dhang ki mulakaat summer play hi tha. "Zindagi badi honi chahiye lambi nhi" ise to bhai ne seriously le liyaüòÇ. Poora college maze maze se jee liya bc. Aur antaragni ke maze to pooch mat (mereüòõ) tujhe dard hua hoga koi na. (Hua na hua na ehh ehh üòõ). Per jo bhi hua, tere nukkad me naye naye characters dekh ke maza bahut aaye, Raja ravish kumar ,CID ki choti choti bakchodiyaan bhai gajab‚ù§. Bahut maje karaye hai bhai. Aur ummid hai aur karne mile. Bas bc sab khatam hoke ek time milne ka mauka mil jaaye, is baar hasta hua DJ khalid banna hai.

author: Piyush

text:
It‚Äôs really hard to express your simplicity and sweetness in words - easily one of the nicest person I know o:)Have seen you inside out (You know what I mean :P)..shouldn‚Äôt go into details on public records. Some things about you really intrigue me - how can someone play all day long (you should be the poster boy of Glucon-D) and have so much organised hostel room (Dude, really WTF!, they are not supposed to be organised in the first place :-)). 
It was a pleasure being your script-writer from Nishika in fresher to Minki in senior year...chutiya tmhara kata...but dukh hmko bhi hua ;)...I guess they didn‚Äôt know you have 6-pack abs, a good job and a kind soul (Khud so jaayenge usko‚Ä¶..)..oh that qualifies you for marriage (already late by Rajasthani standards xD).. can wait to share your rangeen hostel kisse with bhabhi-sa (it‚Äôs time to forget Kristen Stewart).
Your room has always been our backchodi adda...your Gurgaon flat will be one too :) You are better than a bank when it comes to safeguarding money but you used to steal my roomie and his shipment..very bad! ;) Just a friendly reminder - I play better badminton and mini-militia than you. Period. Most probably you would agree, if not, I do have ice cream.
I have got your back just like that Antaragni night dare. Have roamed around a lot together, still, a lot left to explore.  It would be near impossible for someone to know you and not like you for the person you are. Thanks for always being there except PHY103 endsem...hahaha!!. Love you, bro! M just a call away! All the best! A very bright future awaits!
P.S - Is sem to firse dassa aarha hoga !?

text:
You were a hard nut, thankfully I had Meena to help me crack you up. You are a bit moody and sometimes seriously mess up. Hopefully, you remember a few quarrels we had but it turned out fine in the end. Having DOPA as roommate has its own perk and I must say, you have a very well-curated collection :P got a lot of exposure from you -from CCD‚Äôs devils own to good English music, from GOT to the vixen, and many more.

Your attention to minute and keen sense of design is remarkable. Most people here do things that will either fetch good grades or land them a fat job. In that sense, you were very different. Though sometimes overdone, I like your ‚ÄòDoing only things I like‚Äô attitude i.e I remember you watching ‚ÄòThe Office‚Äô instead of studying for Endsem but at the same time putting extra hours to learn Sanskrit and philosophy! 

Do u remember our intense philosophical discussions especially in CCD and those late-night walks afterwards (Wo Jaan Jaan kehke jaan le gye) ?..good old days!  Intelligent to ho hi sir aap bs put your ass to work! All the best! Happy researching! 
B-319 ka tempo high hai!

text:
Abe mujhe nahi laga tha tere liye bhi memoir likhna hai.. Ek tu hi hai jiske liye likhna sabse mushkil hoga.. Jo bhi likhu kam hai aur kuch na kuch reh jaega.. Sabse pehle toh dil se shukriya bc randirona sunne ke liye.. Bc tu nahi hota toh kya hota.. Main main keywords toh tune daal diye. Agar sab keywords daalne baithe toh bhi bhar jaega ye yearbook. Phir bhi dekhte hai..
Gadhi pe hasna, tera oyozone hona, TA ki gand maarna, meri tatti kismat pe rona, paper se pehle sath me hagna, tere bhand hone ke baad baate sunna, Hall 7 toh nahi bhulunga bhai, First year me Pandey ko pareshan karna, OAT ‚ù§Ô∏è, mujhe ulti karake sulane ke liye thanks, mera rr roz sunna, kattar hindu banna (Jai Shree Ram), Pankaj ke maze lena, din bhar tere room me pade rehna, bhai summer kaise bhul gaya tu, kaise pada rehta tha mai tere room me ü§£, roz 12 baje tujhe canteen bulana, Rishab tu aur mai bakchodi karna, tere aur Rishab ke jhagde aur usme mai aag lagata tha ü§£, gandu ek aur bhul gaya tu - Phy103 ke paper ke ek raat pehle library me bakchodi karna, 8-10 bhaiyo pe hasna, MOS dono baar (A ya B toh lag hi jaega madarchod ü§£), class bunk karke ccd canteen jana, Das ki dukaan, tujhe pehli baar daaru pilana, tera bihari naam karan karna, aauga bolna, subah YJHD dekhna aur gaane me background dancer pe hasna...
Aur kitna kuch hai bsdk..
Aakhri ek saal toh isse jyada bakchodi karni hai, ab paisa bhi hoga üòå, pure 4 saal ki khunnas ek me nikal lenge.. Khulega campus bhai.. Bakchodiya baaki hai... College life meri itni bakchod huyi hai aur safal huyi hai toh uska main reason Tu aur Rishab ho.. Love you brother.

PS- Mujhe ab bhi yaad hai pehli baar kaise mile the.. Paki ke room pe tu nanga khada tha aur tab sirf apan dono the jinko Dani pasand thi.. Dani is lub ‚ù§Ô∏è
Tab ye expect nahi kiya tha apan aise dost banege..
(Unexpected friendships are the best ones)
Jaldi mil bsdk. Saal ke upar ho gaya!

text:
Hey Deepak. Roz tera yearbook page kholke baith jaata hu kyuki samajh hi nhi aata kab aur kaha se shuru karu mai. Socha aaj pehla attempt maar hi lu. Toh first draft samajh ke baksh dena :P.

And most importantly, you were always there as a rock for me to fall and rely on. Tere bina toh mai DE courses katai clear nhi kar paata. Raat bhar padna aur phir exam se pehle mujhe padana aur mere doubts clear karna. You even took the blame for me for some of my fuckups in courses! I can't express how grateful I am to have you as a friend during my stay here.

You're the guy who made me fall into love with memes, wholesomeness, shayari, gazal, music and literature. Bhai maine tujhe kitni baar kaha hai, apni kavitao ko publish kar par tu sunta hi nhi -_-. Pata nhi kyu khud ki talent ki kadr hi nhi karta. Thank you for the daily dose of dopamine and serotonin via the memes and music you send my way on a daily basis. Sometimes that is all one needs to drag through their mundane day and life :). 

Keep on spreading happiness man. And ab jaate jaate apne time management ke raaz bhi batate jaa :P. Counselling, HSS, acads, memes aur pata nhi kya kay ek saath sambhal leta hai XO. Thanks for being such an integral part of my campus life.  Bas jald se noida aa phir chill karte apan saath mein :P. Wishing you all the best for your life ahead. And once again, Thank you! ^_^

I have seen you go all out in basketball and badminton to snatch that one basket or that one point against the opponent (which also makes me shit scared at times of being on the same team as you :P). author: Rajan  Singh

text:
Remember the first day of all three of us met for the first time in room 131, 3-Bot. Yaar kitne kush, proud the hum log, after coming to IITK. Reithick ka to pata nahi but apan dono ka to ye tha ki pura muaj masti karni hai. Jitni JEE ke liye mehnat kari hai uska pura badla nikalna hai. Aur tum lag gaye full flow mai, first week mai GOT khatamüòÇ, and then there was no turning back. 

Yaar kisko pata tha ki, hum teeno bhai, ChussŒ≤, King Joffery, Mr R..... , Shubham, Ravi Family ban jayenge. Tumhare sath wo Mili-milaita ke matches (fir usme ladai üòÇ), fir PUBG ke matches ( jo jyada nahi chala fir Mili - Milaita pe aa gaye, Fir se ladai üòÇ), fir Cards ( usme bhi ladai üòÇ) , and then came the monopoly  and uski deals.üòÇüòÇüòÇ. 

Bhai aise hi bita hai pura bachpan. Aisa kehna ki Bahut maza kara bahut jyada nainsafi hogi. Now that I look back I feel that I shouldn't have missed those parties with all you guys instead of weightlifting practice. We should have played more and more Mili - milaita or Monopoly, or anything with you guys. As everything with you all was superfun. 

I really liked your child-like nature of inquisitiveness and curiosity perhaps that is why you were able to get so good marks even after one night of studyüòÇ. With all you guys, you, in particular, I have had some of the best of talks and discussions, which really shaped me as a person. 

Ab mai tere se bat karta hu to lagta hai kitna bada admi ban gaya hai prajwalüòÇüòÇ, Yaar international level competition jeet rahe ho, aur ram jane coding mai kya kya karte rehte ho. But jokes apart am really proud of you, and grateful that I got to spend such a wonderful time of my life with all of you guys.

Lets meet together once again in then you can perhaps give me all the pending parties üòú
author: Rajan  Singh

text:
The coronavirus variant discovered in South Africa can break through the protection provided by Pfizer Inc and BioNTech's COVID-19 vaccine to some extent, a real-world data study in Israel found. However, the variant's prevalence in Israel is very low and the vaccine remains highly effective.

The study was released on the medRxiv pre-print site on April 9 and has not been peer reviewed. It compared almost 400 people who had tested positive for COVID-19, after they received one or two doses of the vaccine, against the same number of unvaccinated patients with the disease.

It matched age and gender, among other characteristics.

The South African variant, B.1.351, was found to make up about 1% of all the COVID-19 cases across all the people studied, according to the study by Tel Aviv University and Israel's largest healthcare provider, Clalit.

But among patients who had received two doses of the vaccine, the variant's prevalence rate was eight times higher than those unvaccinated - 5.4% versus 0.7%.

This suggests the vaccine is less effective against the South African variant, compared with the original coronavirus and a variant first identified in Britain that has come to comprise nearly all COVID-19 cases in Israel, the researchers said.

The researchers said the study was not intended to assess overall vaccine effectiveness against any variant, since it only looked at people who had already tested positive for COVID-19, not at overall infection rates.

Separate real-world Israeli studies on the vaccine's overall effectiveness, including by Clalit, have shown the Pfizer shot to be more than 90% effective. L1N2KU3L6

"We found a disproportionately higher rate of the South African variant among people vaccinated with a second dose, compared to the unvaccinated group. This means that the South African variant is able, to some extent, to break through the vaccine's protection," said Tel Aviv University's Adi Stern.

In an update to the study posted on April 16, the researchers noted that within the group of people who received two doses, which comprised eight people, all of the B.1.351 infections occurred within a week to 13 days after the second shot. None of them tested positive for it 14 days or more after the second dose.

text:
Pappu bhaye!!! First year mein depress rehne se leke F3 mein jaan fukne tak tumne bohot lamba rasta tay kiya hai.

First year mein to yaad hi nahi hai bhaye ki tumne kuchh bola bhi tha XD. Pehli official meeting mein tumne jab 5 minute mein Sachin ka sketch bana diya to seniors ki bhi ruh kaap gayi thi. Are unki chhodo, hume to laga tha ki gaya ye to ab. Lekin tumne sabke muh band kar diye. Shaanti se kaam karke saamne wale ki G maarna koi tumse seekhe. Fir to proper college posters banane lage the tum. Vo ladki kya sahi banayi thi pappu bhaye first year wale room mein. Harlem Shake bhi tumhara hi idea tha. Uske baad se to tumhara swag bas badhta hi gaya. Blue World mein kitne maje kiye the Pappu bhaye apan ne. Sab koi neeche wali slides pe hi jaa rahe the, apan to saari try kar chuke the almost. Ye nunnu nahi kudta to complete kar lete saari. Badhai Ho ke baad ki night photography yaad hai pappu bhaye? Pata nahi kya kya try kiya tha. Tumhara vo gardan wale tareeke se haan bolne ka andaaz alag hi hai. Aur uske saath saath agar muskan bhi mil jaaye tab to sone pe suhaga ho jaaye.

Uss din jab tum bhari garmi mein ganne ka juice leke aaye the sabke liye, tab to alag hi respect badh gayi thi tumhare liye XD. F3 kuchh nahi tha pehle, aaj agar itne logo ke muh pe F3 ka naam hai to bas tumhari wajah se. F3 mein kya kami hai aur usko kaise poora karna hai ye tumse behtar na kabhi koi samajh paaya hai aur na hi kabhi payega. F3 ke maje to kabhi nahi bhool sakte bhaye.

Silently kaam karke apna best effort dena tumhari sabse badi khoobi hai. Aur ye bhi ki tum seedhe muh pe sahi cheez bolte ho (jab bhi bolte ho XP). Apni trip nahi hui Pappu bhaye saath mein abhi tak. Gurgaon se Goa vaise utna zyada dur bhi nahi hai.

text:
Yo ChooseBeta!!! üòÉ
Yaad hai tujhe, first year ke end mein donon ke bhaiyon ne dhokha diya tha agle saal room share karne se. Aur phir uske baad hm donon mile the üòÖ. Dukh mein ek dusre ke saathi!!! Phir uske baad first year summer, 2nd year, 3rd year, bas tu hin tha mujhe jhelne wala ek. üòÇ
Tmlog kitna MM khelte the, aur mujhe uske controls tatti lagte the. Although hmlogon ne badminton, PUBG, cards, Monopoly, aur pata nahin kya kya saath mein khela hai. 
2018 summer mein donon saath mein kaam kiye the on that full-stack development project. Kitni mehnat se tune apna naam dalwaya tha... Aur last day pe BBQ mein party ki thi hmlogon ne üòé.
Then tera fitness enthu, jo 2nd year mein jaaga. Aur tune 5K bhi bhaag liya! 
PUBG mein toh phod dete the sab, jab bhi khelte the saath mein üòé. 
Tu toh apna yoga guru ban gaya tha üòÖüòÖüòÖ. Aise karo, yeh karo, isse yeh hoga, usse woh hoga, ... üôáüèª‚Äç‚ôÇÔ∏è. Aur saath mein diet planner. Tera woh white board par likha hua "kachcha chaba ja" ab bhi wahin likha hai ü§£. 
Tere saath wali Lucknow trip was very memorable. Although non-veg khane ke liye tune mujhe akela chhor diya tha üòï. Aur han, uss shaam ko kaise bhul sakte hain. You went into a mall, changed from jeans to shorts. And then returned back to kanpur in those shorts only ü§£. Telling that these are more comfortable...
Phir teri knee problem and then we saw a completely different Ashish in front of us. Your dedication to come out of it was marvelous. Ab toh tu fitness freak ban gaya hai üòÖ, spending most of your time in gym. Waise ghar mein hin gym kholne ka mera idea tha mast üòé. Ab hme bhi free ka gym gyaan dete rehna üòú.
Waise ek afsos zaroor hoga. Tmse last month mil nahin paane ka... But still, aage milenge toh zaroor mere dost üôåüèª. Phir party karenge...

All the best for the future bro. Aise hin MACHATE raho. Aur hme bhul mat jana üòÖ.

Juniors ki gaand faadni ho, seniors ki gaand jalani ho, batchmate ki gaand leni ho, in sab kaamo ka Gawd hain apna bhai, Kabhi kabhar lagta hain jab kabhi Gand Faadu Ratna ka janm hoga to uska nam hoga Varun Jain Puruskar.

Nostalgia chedna hain kya, bhai apun to humesha sath rhe hain, jab sabhi hall galaxy ki heat me laude lagwa rhe the, tb me or tu side view se inke maje le rhe the, jab kuch log hum dono ke liye aansu baha rhe the tb bhi hum side view se maje le rhe the, jab rendezevous or inter iit har gye the tb bhi hum maje mar rhe theüòÇ

text:
Mai nahi hota to kya hota tera? 
I have literally carried you over the past 4 years. Har cheez ka reminder dena padta hai tujhe. Memoirs likh de ye bhi bolna hi padega I know. Itna careless hai tu. And you had a right to confront me if I failed to carry you xD.
Ek din tujhe uthane ka try kiya, tu nahi utha and TOC ka quiz ho gaya. Kitna sunaya tune mereko bc us baat pe.

Only reason why you‚Äôd be spared from being called ‚Äúthe stingy one‚Äù - Goel. Ek watch khareedne ke liye 10 order karega, use karega fir 9 return karega. Wtf? Who does that? Tera brush karte karte gaane sunne wala dance was epic.

Meri slippers wapas karde.

Also bc tereko har exam se pehle nightout marna rehta tha. Like wtf? Exam se pehle to sona hota hai. Light band hona hoga. How did we even manage all that shit?

I‚Äôm telling you 50 tak job mat karna yaar. Its shit. Live life. I‚Äôll keep on telling you this till 50. 

Funny thing - apan dono Marathi hoke hindi me baat karte hai. I don‚Äôt even know what your Marathi sounds like. Remember how I was unhappy even after getting placed at Plutus? I called Pandey 3-4 times to see if he could do anything to get me into Zomato. Reason? Kyuki tera waha hua tha. Yaar most heartbreaking cheez ki tu Gurgaon and mai Bangalore. Like wtf man? I am actually not ready to comprehend this. Sab bol rhe hai ki touch me rahenge but I don‚Äôt know. Virtual communication is not the same. After all,  I‚Äôm too much used to you. I‚Äôm used to being with you 24/7, used to beating the shit out of you, used to carrying you all your life, used to being shouted at on failing to do so. Chhod bc, mereko referral de dena, mai Zomato aa jaunga. 

Also its crazy how you hadn‚Äôt talked to a single girl in your life before. I‚Äôm sure you gonna be the chick magnet in Gurgaon soon (shakal disagrees but not me). 

I know Goa aane ke liye tereko convince karna was tough but maja aya. Kayaking shit was the best. Also doraemon ki umar me sharaab piyega? Ashish ko batau? 

Ryuzaki >>>> Mochamocha.

P.S. I‚Äôve seen your you-know-what.
P.P.S. Girls reading this, its big.

text:
Where do I start? So, let me start from the beginning. It was CHM101 Lab, I was standing in the front row extreme left and you were front row extreme right. Among everyone in the room, only you asked a few questions to Gurunath. I don‚Äôt remember the questions but that was when I wanted to get to know you. But then fate had it, we met during Arshdeep‚Äôs birthday, CPA, classes, Library, festivals and you became a very important part of my IITK journey. You may not know it but, you have taught me not to simp, you have taught me to read books, you have taught me Pasta is good and also to never stop trying when I fail at something.

I remember I was not at all comfortable with you calling me Paro, but thanks to you, that‚Äôs my new nickname now! And I like it üòÖ. You made me get out of my comfort zone and I cannot thank you enough for that. You had a very major impact on my journey and development through IITK. And how can I forget, you invited me to a movie and you introduced me to Vatsalya. I still remember you and Swastik fighting during the second year Techkriti üòÇ. Such a cute couple. I will miss watching horror movies together (Watch parties are not the same at all). I finally found someone who was more scared than me watching horror movies üòÖ.

Thank you again for everything. All the best for all your future endeavors.
P.S. Let‚Äôs plan to watch another horror movie soon.

text: I borrowed this one from work, and, afraid of doing damage to its white binding, I bought a cloth cover, originally no doubt intended for bibles, to protect the book from smudges or anything else untoward. That covering became symbolic as I dived into this memoir of hiding, transformation, and reversals. In the Darkroom follows feminist scholar Susan Faludi as she reunites with her estranged father, who is now living as a woman in the Budapest of her youth. Her father survived the Holocaust through disguises and subterfuge, then found refuge after the war in depictions of women on film; she is proud to show her daughter the life she has made in Budapest, even as right wing nationalism grows around her. Susan Faludi frankly discusses her struggle to accept her father, both in her estrangement and in her new life as woman, and reading the memoir of an old school feminist figure out how to be trans-inclusive is one of the most heartwarming things you‚Äôll ever come across.

text:
Akshatboi aka ricchie aka chotu
Ye thoda late aaya tha campus mai, to mere ko kaafi uncertainty thi ki yaar kaisa banda hoga, jamming baithegi ki nhi. And then we met. Aur sab kuch kaafi acche se ho gya. Pura saal nikal gya aur pta nhi chala. Kaafi kisse hue. And he bacame an important part of me. I don't share things with lot of people. But he is that person, jiske saath mai sab kuch share krta hu. Our friendship has become too precious for me. Kabhi bhi kuch hota hai, I seek his advice first. Kaafi rational banda hai. Kaafi kuch kiya 4 saalo mai. Even online sem mai bhi kaafi kuch ho gyaüòÖ. 

1st year mai kaafi golu molu tha, pr kaafi kam time mai ekdum slim ho gya. Fully dedicated tha tennis mai, pr saare sports mai accha hai. TA101 ne g**nd le li thi iski. Kaafi courses kare saath mai, kaafi maja aaya, MOS, ERP, DS, ESC201. Sirf 1st year ki Antaragni saath mai attend kri thi, but it was worth it. 1 rajasthan ki trip saath mai ho gyi thi, aur kaafi maja aaya usme, kaafi kisse sunna sunana hua. Verma ki cycle terrace or chahdhayi thi, wo bhi sahi kaa d kiya tha. Khub football khela, aur kaafi kuch seekha bhi isse.

Jyada nhi likhunga, because I think we know and understand each other's importance (aur time bhi kam haiüòÖ). 

Milte hai fatafat se.

ECO101 k tips and guidance wala incident yaad rahega and uske baad k bhi bahot courses/projects k.

Youtube pr gaana loop me laga kr jab tum gaana gaate the tbhi maine tumhe apne band ke liye as a singer recruit kr liya tha. Jldi thoda ab time mile bus aur wapas se maze kr paayein jo krte the. Aapas me humesha ek doosre ko chidhana bus baakiyon ke saamne milkr unko chidhane me kaafi maza aata tha. Thanks for being my bestestest Male (vo samjh rhe ho naa) friend. Apni first conversation hui thi bhoot ki baaton se pr tumhare aawaz joki tum ishq mubaarak gaa rhe the usne mera dhayan aakarshit kiya tha. Jldi se corona khatam ho aur milein toh isi gaane pr ab casio bajayenge (Zara zara toh bhoto baja liye kyun). Chalo padhne jaao ab, kaafi time chala gya tumhara. text:
I am sure everyone knows how hardworking you are, how intelligent you are and yada yada yada (who the f**k doesn't ever get even close to getting a B what the f**k man!).

I still remember the first memory I have of you was the first year when the Prof was trying to derive some detailed result, and midway in his second page he gets stuck. After few minutes of utter silence and confusion, I one guy (out of the odd 400) pointing out that he did a small error somewhere in the first page (!!) of the proof. The image I had of you then is the same I have of you know. Super focused and Super confident.

I think we got to know each other better from the third-semester thermodynamics and in the time we spent together, I have come to know that you are one of the most helpful and honest guys I have ever met (and probably will meet). Sounds cliche? But people often underestimate the importance of being honest to yourself and others in terms of having a long-term friendship. That is something I will take with me forever.

This memoir can't encapsulate how grateful I am for getting me through this undergrad (special mention to that horrible "apping" season of 2019-2020). I would never really understand why you chose to be friends with me, help and guide me in almost all walks of life, and share my love for food and music. 

Although we didn't get the chance to invade our beloved base in the 8th semester (I was anyways planning not to be around in my 7th), you have always been a text away, ready to help/offer your honest criticism. I hope we stay that way forever. Now I know, this won't change anything but please please please please please decide against the K-word we are not allowed to speak about.

Cheers to good times, that were and that will be.

text:
I saw you first time on 22nd July 2017, obviously the first day of IITK. We were in the same cab, And your unique voice can be recognized even in the crowded auditorium of 830 students.
Shuruaat me to koi baat hi nahi hui.. and 3rd year me saath me project mila, you have a dominating nature at that time, jesse tum baat baat par bolti thi ki "Tumse bola tha karne ko to kyu nahi kiya" and kaafi daata tumne uss project me mujhe. 
uske ek saal baad firse project partner ban gaye..üòÇüòÇ coincidentally... iss baar mujhe lag raha tha ki daant to nahi khaani tumhari.. to saara kaam kar diya time se..
CHE352 ke baad socha nahi tha kabhi itne ache dost ban paayenge..

"Maybe you have to know the darkness before you can appreciate the light." and you are much "brighter" and way more mature than I think earlier.

‡§™‡•Ä‡§õ‡•á ‡§ï‡§ø‡§§‡§®‡•Ä ‡§Ø‡§æ‡§¶‡•á ‡§¨‡•Å‡§® ‡§ó‡§Ø‡§æ, ‡§™‡§§‡§æ ‡§π‡•Ä ‡§®‡§æ ‡§ö‡§≤‡§æ !!""

don't think too much ... tum bhot zyada sochti ho choti choti cheezo ke baare me... then pareshaan hoti ho.. 
life ko jiyo jitna jee sakti ho...
I know pichle 4 saal kitni mehnat ki hai tumne..

author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
Sanghi sir, charan sparsh _/\_
First-year ke end me tune bola tha ki 1st year me kaafi chill maar liya ab kaam karta hu pel ke.. fast forward three years.. lo and behold companies are dying to hire you. Mad respect for your dedication and skill and commitment man. Tujhe kaafi indulge karane ki koshish ki tune kabhi interest liya nahi :P Mishrsa se kuch seekh ek baar toh Shiv bhakti dekhni thi tujhe yaar. Aman ko toh ekdum maa ki tarah paala hai bhai tune. Teri bandi ka kya scene tha bhai tune theek se clear kiya nahi mai puchta reh gaya xD Goes without saying that we will be in touch. Kripa banaye rakhna!
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
*drumroll* best of all worlds Neil Shirude!
For the first few years there I think we were just acquaintances but last last me kaaafi ache dost ho gaye apan bhai! Conversations have always been amazing with you and I always learn something new. Pune aane ka bada mann tha yaar COVID spike ke chalte hi reh gaya mera poora mann tha aane ka bhai. Hope tu apni maid se bohot zyada kaam nahi karwa raha hai thoda rest diya kar yaar xD Tu Mumbai/Pune rahega jab tak apna milna ho jayega bhai koi tension nahi hai. TV shows se leke blogs aur books sab cheez pe apan vibe kiye hain. I think apni intellectual frequency kaafi match karti hai (although teri CPI merese bohot zyada hai _/\_ ). Bhai MS jaake insider trading karna bhai London desk hoga tera mai Europe me rahunga :P
Europe trip banani hai bhai apne wale group ki 100% no excuses. Cheers man to the years we've had but more than that looking forward to the years to come. Startup karna hai bhai sath me please please please.
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text: Hows the Kej doing? I hope good. Alright man so I think maine, tune Ayush aur Akshay ne kaafi bakchodi kari hai saath me. Bojack S5E6, ultimate booze, premier nashe aur mess me unlimited debates. Sahi hai yaar tu ekdum full of energy and sparkle. Asehi rehna. Mere paas gyaan bohot hai jab chahiye call kar lena :P Na chahiye toh bhi karna bhai baaten toh hain hi bohot. Hope tera wo chakkar sort out ho gaya hoga, 2nd year me humne kaafi baat kari thi uspe. Oh right uske baad tu alag gali me ghuma tha firse xD (dm agar ishara nahi samjha toh). All right man, have fun keep it simple stay silly.
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
Jaaaneman jaanejahan jaane tamanna! Bhai tu mera bromance hai. It was a happy stoke of luck ki tu mujhe wingie mila warna shayad itna zyada acha dost nahi hota mera aaj ek. Mujhe lagta hai maine IITK ki majority life happenings tujhe hi batayi hai sabse pehle. Do you remember December 2019 before I went to MPI, what a night that was man :') Sorry I broke your laptop that day lol. Bhai raat raat rolls aur dominos se pizza mangwana. First year me shorts me thand me 2 bje Crown burgur jaana, humne toh sath me kitna kuch kiya hai yaar! Tu acha aadmi hai thoda zyada hi sabse bohot achi dosti hai teri isiliye silently har friend circle me all powerful ho jaata hai (although ab maine bhatia aur nikunj ne ye realize kar liya hai :P ) Apna poker table acha set ho gaya hai yaar isko chodenge nahi saalon saal chalayenge! Baaki Covid me ghar pe scene sath me banane ka maza hi aur raha hai yaar XD 
Madhur you have truly been an amazing friend and an indisposable part of my IITK journey. Also good that tune end me Dual drop kar hi diya tujhe kitna samjhaya tha ki pointless hai tere liye :P Bhai SnT Secy banna tha yaar tujhe tu khada hota hum bana hi dete bhai kyu nahi hua. Know that you will always be in my thoughts and prayers and I hope you find a girl soon (or are you more interested in Dikshant?) Europe aao bhai ghumne chalte hain amsterdam. Eastern Europe me *** ka precursor mil jata hai easily udher pure milega bhai mazza aayega! Milte hain jald hi! Time series yaad hai na kya bakchod nikala tha humne xD Presentation lol.
Tera apna,
Kothari
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text: In a 1:16 sex ratio in our batch I had very few female friends and you were one of them. Hum dono aise alag se bohot hangout toh nahi kiye hian but common friends, places me kaafi beaten toh kiye hi hain. I am not sure tu final sem me friendly se 420 friendly hui thi ya nahi par hui thi toh maine miss kardiya yaar, you make very nice insta reels and watching you dance high would have been entertaining! Apan randomly college me mil jaate the toh beaten toh kaafi kar hi lete the, teri vibe botot achi hai Medha stay like this always! Hopefully fir asehi kisi common context me milenge and it will be just as easy for us to hangout as it has always been. Also thank you for clearing out my Facebook friend requests list in ChicBlast lol I had not touched it for years! :P
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
Nachiiii mamaaaa! You may be literally the most striking human being ever man. Tune toh mere IITK life me chaar chand laga diye the bhai. More than two of my exes know you by name (and game) which trust me, is saying a lot. COVID life me bhi ab tune chaar chand laga diye hain bhai jaldi se karde kal hi karde bhai please time lagta hai thoda aane me. Hamari wing ka na ho ke bhi tu hamari wing ka tha bhai, Vedant ke double room me reh hi lena chahiye tha tujhe 3rd year me full time. Tu itna pav kaise kha leta hai?????? Kasol me toh tune kya kya dikha diya bhai mai kabhi nahi bhulunga wo Challal aur Katagla aur baaki random gaon. Freedom is truly hard to find but we found it lol :P
Nice man. Milte rahenge Amsterdam ki trip banani hai jaldi
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:

Tere jokes mein hamesha do teen layers hoti hain and I'm always like ki bc itna kaise sochta hai yeh. Woh gandhi ke room wali party ki raat abhi bhi yaad jab tune gale laga ke rakha tha mujhe kaafi der tak. Tu jitna andar se pyara hai dikhata nhi but deep down bhut pyaara insaan hai tu. From "mereko kaun psnd krega" to "Surat chalte hain" - kaafi bada ho gya hai bc.
Jaldi se PhD ke liye desh chhod main peeche peeche aata hun xD.

Woh cranberry juice trip pe bc, woh acid trip mein red light. Saari parties and trips ki planning krna - hamesha hamare order lena. You are a great friend. Thanks for always being there for me. text:
Yo Mama!!!
I don't remember apan first time kab mile the, but I'm glad that we did. Bhut hi innocent soul hai tu and I love this about you. Hamesha Nayi cheezein try krwata rhta hume - "Arre kuch nhi hoga mama, tu try toh kr". And dheere dheere kab tu wing ka part ban gya pta bhi nhi chala. Kasol trip mein woh monkey cap pehen ke bus ke aage baith ke crush krna xD. The fact that you don't give a fuck to what people think about you is something maine bhut kam logon mein dekha hai. 
Milte hain campus mein and kasol dobara chalte hai xD.

text:
Yugesh bhai - Still remember the first day of college jab tu library nikal gya tha and honestly from the start you were different. First year se hi shayd hi kisi ne itna chaapa hai (atleast amongst the people i know) and aage bhi tu krta hi rhega. Thanks hamesha gyan dene ke liye jab bhi I was down. You are someone I can always look to for advice - chahe acads ho ya trades xD. We haven't talked much in these covid days but I remember that technical conversation with you and Madhur. You are someone to whom I look up to very often. Trip pe bhut bakchodiyan ki hai apan ne, woh police ka bus mein aana and tera bag khulwana jisme sirf gadgets the xD - uski bhi gaand phat gyi itna dekh ke toh.
Hopefully we'll meet sometime soon and Stay the amazing and helpful human  being you are.

PS: Biocon profit mein bech diya tha thanks to you :P.

text: Bhai kahan se shuru krun. Tereko shyd yaad na ho , pehli baar tu mila tha jb tu E-Cell ke event ke liye sbko bulane aaya tha. Phir ek do br tere room pe mila, kya safai rkhta tha bhai tu.
